na%2Fharyana-government-sets-in-motion-demand-of-khaps-for-amendment-in-hindu-marriage-act-534873%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20Additional%20Chief%20Secretary%2C%20Home%20Department%2C%20referred%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20Principal%20Secretary%2C%20Citizen%20Resources%20Information%20Department%20(CRID)%20for%20further%20action%2C%20acting%20on%20the%20demands%20submitted%20by%20the%20Bharat%20Bhoomi%20Bachao%20Sangharsh%20Samiti%20president%20Ramesh%20Dalal%20and%20Sarvjatia%20Kandela%20Khap%20head%20Dharam%20Pal%20Kandela.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20Kandela%20said%20%E2%80%98same-gotra%20and%20same-village%20marriages%20were%20in%20conflict%20with%20the%20social%20norms%20in%20society%E2%80%99%20and%20they%20had%20submitted%20a%20representation%20to%20the%20state%20government%20for%20amendment%20of%20the%20HMA%20in%20line%20with%20the%20khap%20panchayats%E2%80%99%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20intra-gotra%20and%20intra-village%20marriages%20amount%20to%20social%20stigma%2C%20which%20result%20in%20constant%20humiliation%20and%20mental%20torture%20of%20the%20parents%20whose%20boy%2Fgirl%20solemnise%20such%20marital%20ties%20which%20are%20in%20violation%20of%20social%20norms.%20It%20is%20necessary%20to%20bring%20amendments%20in%20the%20HMA%20to%20accommodate%20the%20conditions%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20social%20norms%20for%20maintaining%20the%20social%20fabric%20and%20a%20happy%20family%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kandela%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3ETribune%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDalal%20had%20also%20submitted%20a%20representation%20to%20the%20state%20government%20last%20month%20with%20the%20demand%20that%20in%20addition%20to%20intra-gotra%20and%20intra-village%20marriages%2C%20those%20between%20people%20from%20bordering%20villages%20should%20also%20be%20declared%20invalid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDalal%20said%20he%20was%20assured%20by%20top%20officials%20of%20the%20government%20that%20the%20matter%20had%20been%20assigned%20to%20a%20senior%20official%20who%20was%20likely%20to%20submit%20the%20final%20report%20to%20chief%20minister%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThereafter%2C%20the%20CM%20will%20take%20the%20final%20decision%20on%20the%20demand.%20In%20principle%2C%20the%20government%20was%20in%20agreement%20with%20me%20on%20the%20proposal%20for%20amendment%20in%20the%20HMA%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20paper%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20representation%20was%20submitted%20to%20the%20Haryana%20government%20on%20July%201%2C%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fchandigarh-news%2Fkhap-panchayats-in-haryana-demand-amendment-to-hindu-marriage-act-to-prohibit-same-gotra-marriages-101688410663798.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Nearly%20200%20%3Cem%3Emahapanchayats%3C%2Fem%3E%20have%20been%20organised%20by%20khap%20panchayats%20demanding%20the%20prohibition%20of%20such%20marriages%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691995982000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14121527%2FF3T6TBIb0AAY7VK.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fharyana-govt-to-ban-intra-gotra-intra-village-marriages-as-per-khap-panchayats-demands%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20government%20has%20begun%20the%20process%20of%20amending%20the%20Hindu%20Marriage%20Act%2C%201955.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fharyana-govt-to-ban-intra-gotra-intra-village-marriages-as-per-khap-panchayats-demands%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Has%20Triggered%20Fresh%20Spell%20Of%20Rain%20In%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20heavy%20rain%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Uttarakhand%20over%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20days%20is%20the%20result%20of%20a%20fresh%20spell%20of%20Western%20Disturbance%2C%20the%20weather%20office%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20location%20of%20the%20Monsoon%20trough%20lies%20along%20the%20foothills%20of%20Himalayas%20and%20hence%20the%20South-westerly%20Arabian%20Sea%20monsoonal%20winds%20are%20hitting%20the%20Himalayan%20foothills%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Indian%20Meteorological%20Department%20has%20said%2C%20explaining%20the%20phenomenon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Western%20Disturbance%20refers%20to%20a%20storm%20that%20originates%20in%20the%20Mediterranean%20and%20brings%20heavy%20rain%20to%20mountain%20areas%20in%20the%20Indian%20subcontinent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWeather%20experts%20the%20NDTV%20spoke%20to%20said%20that%20many%20areas%20in%20Himachal%20are%20already%20vulnerable%20following%20the%20monsoon%20fury%20and%20even%20moderate%20rainfall%20in%20these%20areas%20can%20trigger%20landslides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%2021%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Himachal%20over%20the%20past%2048%20hours%20after%20heavy%20rain%20washed%20away%20homes%20and%20triggered%20the%20collapse%20of%20a%20temple%20in%20Shimla.%20The%20temple%20collapse%20has%20claimed%20nine%20lives%20and%20at%20least%2025%20others%20are%20feared%20trapped.%20The%20fresh%20spell%20of%20rain%20has%20triggered%20landslides%2C%20hitting%20road%20connectivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20is%20now%20bracing%20for%20more%20showers%20as%20the%20weather%20office%20has%20predicted%20heavy%20rain%20over%20the%20next%20two%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Sukhwinder%20Singh%20Sukhu%20has%20appealed%20to%20people%20to%20stay%20indoors%20and%20said%20efforts%20to%20restore%20connectivity%20at%20the%20earliest%20are%20being%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Uttarakhand%2C%20heavy%20rain%20has%20caused%20loss%20to%20property.%20A%20video%20showing%20floodwaters%20wash%20away%20a%20multi-storeyed%20college%20building%20has%20gone%20viral%2C%20capturing%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20calamity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlaknanda%2C%20Mandakini%20and%20Ganga%20rivers%20are%20flowing%20above%20the%20danger%20level%20at%20Rudraprayag%2C%20Shrinagar%20and%20Devprayag%2C%20the%20disaster%20control%20room%20in%20Dehradun%20said.%20The%20Badrinath%20National%20highway%20is%20blocked%20at%20several%20places%20due%20to%20landslides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fresh%20spell%20of%20torrential%20rain%20comes%20as%20the%20hill%20states%20were%20limping%20back%20to%20normalcy%20following%20the%20monsoon%20fury%20a%20month%20back%20that%20led%20to%20huge%20loss%20of%20life%20and%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691995980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F64gd8tao_himachal-rain_625x300_14_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhimachal-rain-update-himachal-rain-himachal-live-uttarakhand-rain-uttarakhand-rain-update-what-has-triggered-fresh-spell-of-rain-in-uttarakhand-himach-4296080%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20heavy%20rain%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Uttarakhand%20over%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20days%20is%20the%20result%20of%20a%20fresh%20spell%20of%20Western%20Disturbance%2C%20the%20weather%20office%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhimachal-rain-update-himachal-rain-himachal-live-uttarakhand-rain-uttarakhand-rain-update-what-has-triggered-fresh-spell-of-rain-in-uttarakhand-himach-4296080%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhimachal-rain-update-himachal-rain-himachal-live-uttarakhand-rain-uttarakhand-rain-update-what-has-triggered-fresh-spell-of-rain-in-uttarakhand-himach-4296080%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhimachal-rain-update-himachal-rain-himachal-live-uttarakhand-rain-uttarakhand-rain-update-what-has-triggered-fresh-spell-of-rain-in-uttarakhand-himach-4296080%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chandrayaan-3%20gets%20closer%20to%20100km%20circular%20orbit%3B%201%20move%20away%20before%20Vikram%20separation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691995839000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102715318%2Cimgsize-87894.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fchandrayaan-3-gets-closer-to-100km-circular-orbit-1-move-away-before-vikram-separation%2Farticleshow%2F102715383.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Isro%20has%20reduced%20the%20altitude%20of%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20spacecraft%20to%20under%20200km%20using%20a%20planned%20manoeuvre%2C%20with%20a%20further%20one%20planned%20for%2016%20August%2C%20which%20will%20take%20the%20spacecraft%20into%20a%20circular%20orbit%20of%20100km%2C%20before%20the%20lander%20separates%20on%2017%20August.%20A%20critical%20analysis%20of%20each%20of%20the%20manoeuvres%20being%20performed%20will%20assess%20the%20potential%20risks%20of%20close%20approaches%20with%20the%20other%20lunar%20orbiters.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22CHETHAN%20KUMAR%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A54%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fchandrayaan-3-gets-closer-to-100km-circular-orbit-1-move-away-before-vikram-separation%2Farticleshow%2F102715383.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Don't%20Take%20Your%20Life%2C%20NEET%20Will%20Be%20Scrapped%5C%22%3A%20MK%20Stalin%20Assures%20Students%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20M%20K%20Stalin%20on%20Monday%20passionately%20appealed%20to%20National%20Eligibility-cum-Entrance%20Test%20(NEET)%20aspirants%20not%20to%20harbour%20any%20suicidal%20tendencies%20but%20face%20life%20with%20self-confidence%2C%20after%20a%20medical%20aspirant%20allegedly%20ended%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Stalin%20claimed%20that%20in%20a%20few%20months%2C%20when%20the%20political%20change%20takes%20place%2C%20then%20the%20NEET%20barriers%20will%20come%20crashing%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%2C%20all%20those%20who%20say%20'I%20will%20not%20sign'%20will%20disappear%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20apparently%20referring%20to%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Governor%20RN%20Ravi's%20remarks%20against%20the%20state's%20anti-NEET%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20offer%20my%20deepest%20condolences%20on%20the%20demise%20of%20student%20Jagatheeswaran%20and%20his%20father%20Selvasekhar%20(who%20also%20allegedly%20died%20by%20suicide).%20Let%20their%20deaths%20be%20the%20last%20on%20the%20altar%20of%20NEET%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Stalin%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20shock%20over%20the%20recent%20demise%20of%20the%20medical%20aspirant%20Jagatheeswaran%2C%20a%20student%20from%20Chromepet%20in%20the%20city%20who%20unsuccessfully%20attempted%20to%20clear%20the%20entrance%20test%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20he%20was%20at%20a%20loss%20to%20console%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJagatheeswaran's%20father%20Selvasekhar%20also%20committed%20suicide%20the%20next%20day.%20I%20am%20at%20a%20loss%20on%20how%20to%20console%20his%20family%20and%20friends%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20parents%20wanted%20to%20see%20their%20son%2C%20who%20studied%20well%2C%20as%20a%20medical%20doctor.%20But%20Jagadeeswaran%20%26quot%3Bhas%20joined%20the%20list%20of%20victims%20on%20the%20altar%20of%20NEET%20exam%2C%20which%20is%20the%20most%20gruesome%20incident%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20spate%20of%20alleged%20NEET-related%20suicides%20have%20been%20reported%20in%20the%20state%20in%20the%20past%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20appeal%20that%20no%20student%20should%20ever%20make%20a%20decision%20to%20take%20away%20their%20own%20lives%20under%20any%20circumstances.%20The%20NEET%2C%20which%20is%20a%20hurdle%20for%20your%20growth%2C%20will%20be%20scrapped.%20The%20state%20government%20is%20actively%20working%20on%20the%20legal%20initiative%20in%20this%20direction%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Stalin%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20Assembly%20resolutions%20demanding%20NEET%20exemption%20for%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20he%20said%20the%20Governor%20returned%20the%20first%20resolution%20and%20sent%20the%20second%20one%20to%20the%20President%20for%20assent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20appears%20that%20Governor%20Ravi%20wants%20the%20bill%20to%20be%20shelved.%20NEET%20exam%20has%20become%20expensive%20and%20can%20be%20afforded%20only%20by%20the%20rich%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20cannot%20afford%20to%20study%20by%20spending%20huge%20sums%20of%20money%20failed%20in%20the%20test%2C%20he%20claimed%20and%20said%20a%20situation%20has%20arisen%20wherein%20those%20who%20qualify%20NEET%20alone%20can%20join%20a%20medical%20college%20if%20they%20have%20money%20and%20that%20medical%20education%20is%20only%20for%20those%20who%20have%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20spite%20of%20this%2C%20the%20state%20government%20brought%207.5%20percent%20reservation%20for%20the%20poor%20students%20of%20government%20schools%20in%20medical%20colleges.%20But%2C%20the%20Governor%20refuses%20to%20understand.%20There%20is%20a%20doubt%20that%20he%20is%20acting%20like%20a%20puppet%20of%20the%20coaching%20centers%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Stalin%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccusing%20Mr%20Ravi%20of%20%26quot%3Bconducting%20classes%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20by%20inviting%20students%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20claimed%20the%20Governor%20%26quot%3Bdisplayed%20his%20ignorance%26quot%3B%20when%20he%20had%20remarked%20that%20he%20would%20not%20sign%20the%20NEET%20exemption%20bill%2C%20an%20issue%20raised%20by%20a%20student's%20father%20from%20Salem%20during%20an%20interaction%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bill%20does%20not%20await%20his%20signature.%20It%20rests%20with%20the%20President.%20Governor%20has%20no%20authority%20as%20far%20as%20this%20is%20concerned%2C%20though%20he%20is%20giving%20the%20impression%20that%20he%20wields%20authority.%20No%20matter%20how%20many%20lives%20are%20lost%20like%20that%20of%20Jagadeeswaran%2C%20the%20heart%20of%20Governor%20RN%20Ravi%20will%20not%20melt.%20Human%20life%20has%20no%20value%20in%20the%20times%20of%20such%20stone-hearted%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Stalin%20said%20offering%20his%20deepest%20condolences%20to%20bereaved%20family%20of%20Jagatheeswaran%20and%20his%20father%20Selvasekhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20their%20death%20be%20the%20final%20one%20on%20the%20altar%20of%20NEET.%20A%20bright%20future%20awaits%20you%20students.%20Be%20self-confident.%20Live%20and%20let%20others%20live.%20I%20urge%20you%20once%20again%20don't%20harbour%20any%20suicidal%20tendencies%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Cthead%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Cth%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3EHelplines%3C%2Fth%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Fthead%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3EVandrevala%20Foundation%20for%20Mental%20Health%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B919999666555%5C%22%3E9999666555%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ahelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%5C%22%3Ehelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3ETISS%20iCall%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B912225521111%5C%22%3E022-25521111%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Monday-Saturday%3A%208%20am%20to%2010%20pm)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%20%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E(If%20you%20need%20support%20or%20know%20someone%20who%20does%2C%20p