ather%20Found%20Dead%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20his%2019-year-old%20son%20died%20by%20suicide%20after%20failing%20to%20clear%20the%20NEET%20medical%20entrance%20exam%2C%20the%20boy's%20father%20was%20found%20dead%20at%20his%20home%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Chennai%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJagadeeswaran%2C%20who%20had%20graduated%20from%20Class%20XII%20in%202022%20with%20427%20marks%2C%20was%20unable%20to%20clear%20the%20entrance%20in%20two%20attempts.%20On%20Saturday%2C%20he%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20calls%20from%20his%20father%20and%20was%20found%20dead%20at%20home.%20His%20father%2C%20Selvasekar%2C%20was%20found%20dead%20the%20next%20morning.%20Unable%20to%20cope%20with%20the%20grief%20of%20his%20son's%20death%2C%20Selvasekar%20hanged%20himself%20at%20his%20home%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20condoled%20the%20deaths%20and%20appealed%20to%20students%20%26quot%3Bto%20not%20entertain%20suicidal%20thoughts%20but%20to%20have%20self-confidence%20and%20to%20live%20life%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20assembly%20passed%20a%20bill%20seeking%20exemption%20from%20NEET%2C%20arguing%20that%20it%20favors%20affluent%20students%20who%20can%20afford%20private%20coaching%20and%20puts%20students%20from%20poor%20families%20and%20rural%20areas%20at%20a%20disadvantage%2C%20even%20if%20they%20score%20high%20marks%20in%20their%20Class%20XII%20exams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20nearly%20a%20decade%20prior%20to%20this%2C%20the%20state%20had%20abolished%20entrance%20tests%20for%20medical%20admissions%20and%20admitted%20students%20to%20MBBS%20programs%20based%20on%20their%20Class%20XII%20marks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernor%20RN%20Ravi%2C%20who%20had%20returned%20the%20bill%20after%20a%20long%20delay%2C%20forwarded%20it%20to%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20after%20the%20assembly%20passed%20it%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Sta