has%20even%20eclipsed%20the%20entirety%20of%20One%20Direction%E2%80%99s%20gross%20figures%20during%20the%20years%20they%20toured%20from%202012%20to%202015.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Flove-on-tour-by-harry-styles-concludes-with-astronomical-worldwide-figures-of-617-3-million%2Farticleshow%2F102713681.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98They%20Had%20No%20Idea%20How%20Gay%20People%20Exist%E2%80%99%3A%20Queer%20Comedian%20Breaks%20Barriers%20in%20Comedy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENavin%20Noronha%2C%20a%2031-year-old%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F153761%2Fdeepika-mhatre-mumbai-domestic-help-stand-up-comedian%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estand-up%20comic%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20podcaster%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20was%2014%20when%20he%20knew%20he%20was%20queer%20(gay).%20But%20he%20was%20also%20raised%20as%20a%20staunch%20Catholic.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20tried%20to%20first%20do%20away%20with%20that%20%5Bfeeling%20attracted%20to%20boys%5D%20by%20joining%20Bible%20camps.%20When%20I%20was%20in%20Class%208%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20priests%20coming%20to%20our%20church%20recognised%20me%20as%20a%20very%20talented%20and%20outspoken%20child.%20At%20a%20very%20young%20age%2C%20I%20was%20groomed%20to%20become%20a%20Catholic%20priest.%20But%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20realised%20I%20like%20men%20and%20that%20duality%20set%20in.%20So%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20say%20anything%20about%20it%20for%20a%20very%20long%20time%20until%20I%20was%2019%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Navin%2C%20speaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavin%20first%20came%20out%20to%20his%20best%20friend%20Amit%2C%20who%20he%20knew%20since%20they%20were%2010.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20already%20knew%20each%20other%20very%20well%2C%20although%20we%20were%20never%20friends%20who%20spoke%20about%20personal%20stuff.%20So%2C%20when%20I%20came%20out%20to%20him%2C%20it%20was%20only%20a%20matter%20of%20fact.%20I%20just%20kind%20of%20came%20out%20to%20him%20and%20nothing%20changed%20after%20that%20because%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20being%20gay%20is%20really.%20People%20who%20know%20you%2C%20know%20you%20for%20who%20you%20are.%20What%20gender%20you%20sleep%20with%20barely%20makes%20a%20difference%20to%20them%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20he%20was%2021%20and%20in%20his%20third%20year%20of%20college%2C%20he%20had%20come%20out%20to%20most%20of%20his%20friends.%20He%20says%20he%20felt%20the%20need%20to%20tell%20all%20his%20friends%20and%20acquaintances%20that%20he%20was%20gay%20because%20he%20had%20begun%20feeling%20left%20out%20from%20their%20conversations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20also%20wanted%20to%20chime%20in%2C%20but%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20people%20would%20share%20weird%20notions%20of%20what%20gay%20people%20are%20with%20me.%20Listening%20to%20them%2C%20I%20found%20some%20of%20their%20notions%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F152754%2Fiit-madras-kaushik-section-377-supreme-court%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egay%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20hilarious.%20They%20had%20no%20idea%20about%20gay%20people%20and%20how%20we%20exist.%20That%20became%20the%20subject%20of%20my%20first%20comedy%20set%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FNavin-Noronha-01-1691803028.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Queer%20Comedian%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploa