arendra%20Modi%2C%20then%20she%20will%20win%20for%20sure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVaranasi%20people%20want%20Priyanka%20Gandhi.%20If%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20contests%20from%20Varanasi%20against%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20then%20she%20will%20win%20for%20sure.%20Varanasi%20people%20want%20Priyanka%20Gandhi.%20The%20fight%20for%20Raebareli%2C%20Varanasi%2C%20and%20Amethi%20is%20tough%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Raut%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20he%20said%20that%20if%20former%20Pakistan%20Prime%20Minister%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20could%20meet%2C%20then%20why%20not%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20speculations%20of%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar%20meeting%2C%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20has%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20and%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20can%20meet%2C%20then%20why%20not%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar%3F%20We%20get%20to%20know%20from%20the%20media%20that%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar%20met%20yesterday%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%20will%20speak%20on%20it%20soon.%20I%20think%20Sharad%20Pawar%20invited%20Ajit%20Pawar%20for%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20meeting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raut%20also%20said%20that%20even%20both%20Deputy%20CMs%20of%20Maharashtra%20are%20not%20happy%20with%20this%20current%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnything%20can%20happen%20in%20politics.%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20and%20the%20people%20of%20Maharashtra%20are%20not%20happy%20with%20this%20current%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20chief%20Sharad%20Pawar%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20'secret%20meeting'%20with%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20on%20which%20he%20said%20how%20the%20meeting%20became%20a%20secret%20when%20it%20was%20held%20at%20someone's%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20wrong%20with%20meeting%20my%20nephew%3F%20How%20it%20can%20become%20secret%20when%20it%20was%20held%20at%20someone's%20residence.%20I%20was%20there%20at%20his%20residence%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjit%20Pawar%2C%20nephew%20of%20Sharad%20Pawar%20along%20with%20eight%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20MLAs%2C%20switched%20over%20to%20the%20BJP-Shiv%20Sena%20(Eknath%20Shinde)-led%20Maharashtra%20government%20recently.%20Ajit%20Pawar%20later%20claimed%20to%20have%20support%20from%20several%20MLAs%20of%20NCP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20then%20sworn%20in%20as%20a%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20the%20state.%20Maharashtra's%20other%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20BJP's%20Devendra%20Fadnavis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691985420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F62mmdjg4_priyanka-gandhi-1200_625x300_12_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpriyanka-gandhi-sanjay-raut-pm-narendra-modi-varanasi-lok-sabha-seat-if-priyanka-gandhi-contests-from-varanasi-sanjay-rauts-big-claim-4295738%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray%20faction)%20leader%20Sanjay%20Raut%20has%20claimed%20that%20if%20Congress%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20contests%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20from%20Varanasi%2C%20the%20constituency%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20then%20she%20will%20win%20for%20sure%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A30%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpriyanka-gandhi-sanjay-raut-pm-narendra-modi-varanasi-lok-sabha-seat-if-priyanka-gandhi-contests-from-varanasi-sanjay-rauts-big-claim-4295738%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpriyanka-gandhi-sanjay-raut-pm-narendra-modi-varanasi-lok-sabha-seat-if-priyanka-gandhi-contests-from-varanasi-sanjay-rauts