3EHimachal%20Pradesh%20has%20been%20the%20worst%20affected%20state%20in%20the%20country%20due%20to%20the%20floods%20and%20landslides%20with%20officials%20announcing%20a%20staggering%20loss%20of%20Rs%207020.28%20crore%20due%20to%20the%20monsoon's%20devastating%20impact%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20monsoon%20season%20commenced%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20on%20June%2024.%20According%20to%20the%20officials%2C%20the%20monsoon's%20death%20count%20stands%20at%20257%20lives%20lost%20due%20to%20a%20range%20of%20causes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COf%20the%20257%2C%2066%20people%20lost%20their%20lives%20due%20to%20landslides%20and%20flash%20floods.%20191%20people%20lost%20their%20lives%20due%20to%20road%20accidents%20or%20other%20reasons.%20While%2032%20people%20are%20missing%20and%20290%20people%20have%20been%20injured%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20officials%20informed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20as%20per%20the%20official%20inputs%2C%201376%20houses%20have%20been%20damaged%20in%20the%20state%20while%207935%20houses%20have%20been%20partially%20damaged%20so%20far%20in%20the%20monsoon%20havoc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C270%20shops%20have%20been%20damaged%20amid%20monsoon%20and%202727%20cow%20sheds%20have%20been%20damaged%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20official%20data%2C%20the%20state%20so%20far%20witnessed%2090%20landslides%20and%2055%20flash%20flood%20incidents.%20While%20still%20nearly%20450%20roads%20including%202%20National%20Highways%20are%20closed%20in%20the%20state.%201814%20electricity%20supply%20schemes%20are%20still%20Hampered%20and%2059%20water%20supply%20schemes%20are%20still%20disrupted%2C%20the%20officials%20informed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20view%20of%20the%20incessant%20rains%2C%20the%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20government%20on%20Sunday%20informed%20that%20all%20educational%20institutions%20in%20the%20state%20will%20remain%20closed%20on%20August%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Sukhwinder%20Singh%20Sukhu%20has%20taken%20this%20decision%20in%20view%20of%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20students%20due%20to%20heavy%20rains.%20On%20the%20orders%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20the%20Education%20Secretary%20has%20issued%20a%20notification%20to%20keep%20all%20government%2C%20private%20schools%20and%20colleges%20closed%20on%20August%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20also%20took%20feedback%20from%20all%20the%20District%20Collectors%20(DC)%20about%20the%20damage%20caused%20due%20to%20heavy%20rains%20in%20the%20districts.%20He%20also%20got%20information%20about%20the%20closure%20of%20the%20road%20routes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20learned%20about%20the%20damage%20caused%20by%20landslides%20and%20damage%20to%20houses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CM%20has%20instructed%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%2C%20Home%20Secretary%20as%20well%20as%20all%20DCs%20to%20keep%20a%20close%20watch%20on%20the%20situation%20created%20due%20to%20heavy%20rains.%20The%20administrative%20staff%20should%20be%20alert%20and%20maintain%20smooth%20arrangements%20for%20roads%2C%20electricity%20and%20water%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20of%20the%20state%20issued%20a%20notification%20informing%20that%20all%20the%20ongoing%20examinations%20of%20Post%20Graduate%20classes%20including%20B.Ed%20exams%20scheduled%20on%20August%2014%20have%20been%20cancelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20for%20the%20information%20of%20all%20concerned%20and%20worthy%20Principals%20of%20colleges%20affiliated%20and%20maintained%20by%20HP%20University%20that%20keeping%20in%20view%20the%20incessant%20rains%20and%20inclement%20weather%20conditions%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20University%20has%20decided%20to%20cancel%20all%20the%20ongoing%20examinations%20of%20Post%20Graduate%20classes%20including%20B.%20Ed.%20exams%20scheduled%20on%20August%2014%20only%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20notification%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20landslides%20after%20heavy%20rains%20during%20the%20last%20few%20days%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh's%20Shimla%20have%20created%20havoc%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHouses%20in%20many%20areas%20face%20threat%20due%20to%20the%20landslides%20and%20the%20Shimla%20Municipal%20Corporation%20on%20Sunday%20issued%20a%20notice%20for%20vacation%20as%20a%20major%20landslide%20in%20the%20Himland%20area%20has%20caused%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20houses%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20landslides%20happened%20and%20the%20structure%20is%20loose%20and%20our%20preliminary%20observation%20is%20that%20it%20is%20not%20safe.%20Seven%20occupants%20are%20living%20here.%20We%20have%20issued%20an%20advisory%20to%20all%20seven%20occupants%20by%20way%20of%20notice%20serving%20to%20them%20and%20they%20have%20agreed%20and%20vacated.%20We%20have%20told%20them%20until%20the%20report%20for%20safety%20is%20not%20issued%2C%20this%20place%20is%20not%20safe%20to%20live%2C%20all%20have%20vacated%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mahboob%20Sheiq%2C%20Architect%20Planner%2C%20Shimla%20Municipal%20Corporation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20local%20resident%20said%20that%20they%20are%20feeling%20unsafe%20and%20are%20in%20a%20state%20of%20fear%20as%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20(IMD)%20has%20predicted%20more%20rain%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20because%20of%20the%20structure%20problem%2C%20the%20water%20discharge%20was%20not%20proper%2C%20it%20happened%20at%20around%20quarter%20to%206%20AM.%20We%20have%20vacated%20the%20houses%2C%20the%20people%20from%20the%20administration%20have%20come%20and%20offered%20temporary%20shelters%20so%20far%20we%20will%20manage%20with%20our%20own%20arrangement%2C%E2%80%9D%20KC%20Katoch%2C%20a%20local%20resident%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20several%20roads%2C%20which%20were%20earlier%20blocked%20due%20to%20landslides%20and%20other%20rain-related%20incidents%2C%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh's%20Solan%20district%2C%20have%20been%20re-opened%20for%20traffic%2C%20the%20district%20authorities%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20includes%20major%20roads%20along%20the%20National%20Highway-05%2C%20National%20Highway-205%20and%20also%20that%20are%20near%20National%20Highway-907A.On%20NH-05%2C%20around%2011%20roads%20have%20been%20cleared%20and%20opened%20for%20traffic.%20However%2C%20on%20some%20of%20them%2C%20only%20one%20lane%20has%20been%20opened%20for%20vehicular%20movement.%20This%20includes%20Parwanoo-Datyar%20road%3B%20Datyar-Chakimore%20road%3B%20Chakimore-Jabli%20road%3B%20and%20Jabli-Dharampur%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20Meteorological%20Centre%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20has%20predicted%20that%20moderate%20to%20heavy%20rainfall%20is%20very%20likely%20to%20continue%20over%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20IMD%20statement%2C%20moderate%20to%20heavy%20rainfall%20at%20many%20places%20is%20very%20likely%20to%20continue%20over%20the%20state%20with%20very%20heavy%20to%20extremely%20heavy%20rainfall%20at%20isolated%20places%20in%20the%20district%20of%20Chamba%20Kangra%20Hamirpur%20Mandi%20Bilaspur%20Solan%20Shimla%20Kullu%20and%20Sirmaur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20forecasted%20very%20heavy%20rainfall%20at%20many%20places%20and%20extremely%20heavy%20rainfall%20at%20isolated%20places%20in%20Beas%2C%20Ranjit%20Sagar%20and%20the%20Pong%20dam%20catchment%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHeavy%20rainfall%20at%20many%20places%20with%20very%20heavy%20rainfall%20at%20isolated%20places%20in%20Sutlej%20catchment%20area%26quot%3B%2C%20IMD%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691963700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Foo6p8o2g_himachal-rain_625x300_30_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F257-d