.%20One%20is%20pushed%20to%20a%20point%20where%20the%20only%20way%20one%20can%20save%20one%E2%80%99s%20dignity%20is%20by%20resigning.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CWe%20know%20that%20a%20lot%20went%20on%20behind%20closed%20doors%E2%80%9D%20before%20Das%20put%20in%20his%20papers%2C%20a%20second%20Ashoka%20academic%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20third%20faculty%20member%20familiar%20with%20the%20development%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20been%20trying%20as%20hard%20as%20possible%20to%20get%20him%20to%20stay%E2%80%A6.%20He%20has%20submitted%20his%20resignation.%20We%E2%80%99re%20trying%20to%20persuade%20him%20to%20stay.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAshoka%20took%20public%20stand%20on%20paper%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENews%20of%20Das%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20is%20likely%20to%20reignite%20concerns%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaacademicfreedom.net%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estate%20of%20academic%20freedom%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshoka%20University%20raised%20eyebrows%20last%20week%20when%20it%20pointedly%20distanced%20itself%20from%20his%20research%20and%20implicitly%20questioned%20its%20quality%20by%20saying%20that%20%E2%80%9CAshoka%20values%20research%20that%20is%20critically%20peer-reviewed%20and%20published%20in%20reputed%20journals.%20To%20the%20best%20of%20our%20knowledge%2C%20the%20paper%20in%20question%20has%20not%20yet%20completed%20a%20critical%20review%20process%20and%20has%20not%20been%20published%20in%20an%20academic%20journal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20university%E2%80%99s%20stand%20drew%20criticism%20from%20students%20and%20academics%2C%20especially%20given%20the%20track%20record%20of%20how%20it%20had%20handled%20its%20reputed%20vice%20chancellor%20Pratap%20Bhanu%20Mehta%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fpratap-bhanu-mehta-resigns-as-professor-at-ashoka-university%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520a%2520letter%2520to%2520students%2CVC%2520rather%2520than%2520stop%2520writing.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhen%20he%20was%20both%20nudged%20and%20persuaded%20to%20resign%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20March%202021%20due%20to%20his%20media%20writings%20on%20the%20politics%20of%20the%20ruling%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20critic%20called%20Ashoka%E2%80%99s%20comment%20on%20Das%E2%80%99s%20paper%20an%20example%20of%C2%A0%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theindiacable.com%2Fi%2F135712802%2Fashoka-universitys-response-to-its-own-faculty-is-democratic-backsliding-in-academia%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98democratic%20backsliding%20in%20academia%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fashoka-university-resignations-kashmir%5C%22%3Eallegations%20had%20been%20levelled%20by%20the%20faculty%20council%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20founders%20had%20asked%20two%20members%20of%20the%20faculty%20%E2%80%93%20deputy%20manager%20of%20academic%20affairs%20Saurav%20Goswami%20and%20programme%20manager%20of%20academic%20affairs%20Adil%20Mushtaq%20Shah%20%E2%80%93%20to%20resign%20in%202016%2C%20over%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20had%20signed%20a%20petition%20against%20violence%20in%20Kashmir%20after%20Burhan%20Wani%E2%80%99s%20death%20and%20demanded%20a%20plebiscite%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20called%20research%20%E2%80%98half-baked%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDas%E2%80%99s%20paper%20triggered%20a%20debate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Flok-sabha-election-commission-manipulated-evm-fraud%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewith%20former%20civil%20servant%20MG%20Devasahayam%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20psephologists-politicians%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fopinion%2Fsomething-was-fishy-about-2019-polls-for-sure-but-dont-expect-das-paper-to-catch-the-fish%2F1705846%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EYogendra%20Yadav%20praising%20it%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20%E2%80%9Cdrawing%20attention%E2%80%9D%20to%20anomalies%20in%20the%20election%2C%20and%20others%20like%20Nalin%20Mehta%2C%20author%20of%20a%20recent%20book%20on%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-four-reasons-why-ashoka-university-researchers-claims-about-manipulation-in-2019-polls-are-misleading-8500609.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Equestioning%20his%20methodology%20and%20findings%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fnational%2F-democratic-backsliding-in-india-ashoka-university-faculty-s-paper-stirs-major-row-with-electoral-manipulation-charge-news-309827%5C%22%3EBJP%20leaders%20made%20scathing%20comments%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20spared%20neither%20Das%20nor%20Ashoka%20University%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20fine%20to%20differ%20with%20the%20BJP%20on%20matters%20of%20policy%20but%20this%20is%20taking%20it%20too%20far%E2%80%A6how%20can%20someone%20in%20the%20name%20of%20half-baked%20research%20discredit%20India%E2%80%99s%20vibrant%20poll%20process%3F%20How%20can%20any%20University%20allow%20it%3F%20Answers%20needed-%20this%20is%20not%20good%20enough%20a%20response.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20Malviya%2C%20the%20convenor%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20IT%20cell%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20research%20paper%20by%20Ashoka%20University%E2%80%99s%20Sabyasachi%20Das%20presents%20several%20datasets%20and%20dozens%20of%20charts%20as%20%E2%80%98evidence%E2%80%99%20of%20what%20he%20calls%20%E2%80%98significant%20irregularities%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98electoral%20fraud%E2%80%99.%20These%20are%20big%20claims.%20Does%20the%20evidence%20stack%20up%3F%20The%20answer%20is%20No%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20abstract%20of%20Das%E2%80%99s%20study%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20paper%20contributes%20to%20the%20discussion%20by%20documenting%20irregular%20patterns%20in%20the%202019%20general%20election%20in%20India%20and%20identifying%20whether%20they%20are%20due%20to%20electoral%20manipulation%20or%20precise%20control%2C%20i.e.%2C%20%5Bthe%5D%20incumbent%20party%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20precisely%20predict%20and%20affect%20win%20margins%20through%20campaigning.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20compile%20several%20new%20datasets%20and%20present%20evidence%20that%20is%20consistent%20with%20electoral%20manipulation%20in%20closely%20contested%20constituencies%20and%20is%20less%20supportive%20of%20the%20precise%20control%20hypothesis.%20The%20manipulation%20appears%20to%20take%20the%20form%20of%20targeted%20electoral%20discrimination%20against%20India%E2%80%99s%20largest%20minority%20group%20%E2%80%93%20Muslims%2C%20partly%20facilitated%20by%20weak%20monitoring%20by%20election%20observers.%20The%20results%20present%20a%20worrying%20development%20for%20the%20future%20of%20democracy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshoka%20University%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.the-edict.in%2Fpost%2Fdebate-and-attacks-surround-sabyasachi-das-working-paper-on-democratic-backsliding%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estudent%20newspaper%2C%20The%20Edict%20captured%20the%20nuances%20of%20the%20debate%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20underlining%20that%20the%20Economics%20department%20issued%20no%20statement%20and%20the%20stand%20of%20its%20faculty%20on%20Das%E2%80%99s%20conclusions%20is%20not%20known.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESabyasachi%20Das%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ashoka.edu.in%2Fprofile%2Fsabyasachi-das%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECV%20on%20the%20Ashoka%20website%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20that%20he%20has%20received%20his%20Ph.D.%20in%20Economics%20at%20Yale%20University%20in%202015.%20Prior%20to%20joining%20Ashoka%20University%20he%20was%20a%20postdoctoral%20fellow%20at%20the%20prestigious%20Indian%20Statistical%20Institute%2C%20Delhi.%20His%20fields%20of%20specialisation%20are%20political%20economy%2C%20public%20economics%2C%20and%20applied%20microeconomics.%20For%20his%20research%2C%20he%20is%20primarily%20interested%20in%20exploring%20group%20inequalities%20that%20emerge%20from%20various%20democratic%20processes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20his%20CV%2C%20%E2%80%9Che%20has%20studied%20gender%20and%20caste%20issues%20in%20village%20elections%20and%20meetings%20in%20India%2C%20and%20explored%20governance%20consequences%20of%20political%20alignment%20between%20state%20and%20local%20governments%20by%20looking%20at%20appointments%20of%20bureaucrats.%20In%20other%20work%2C%20he%20is%20exploring%20broad%20electoral%20systems%2C%20such%20plurality%20rule%20and%20proportional%20representation%2C%20and%20comparing%20them%20across%20countries%20to%20determine%20their%20effect%20on%20representation%20of%20minorities%20in%20the%20government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENote%3A%20This%20is%20a%20developing%20story%20and%20is%20being%20updated%20as%20more%20information%20comes%20in.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691955401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14005619%2Fcollage.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fauthor-of-paper-on-possible-manipulation-in-2019-polls-quits-ashoka-university%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sabyasachi%20Das%E2%80%99s%20paper%20was%20attacked%20by%20BJP%20leaders%20and%20the%20university%20quickly%20distanced%20itself%20from%20his%20study%2C%20prompting%20accusations%20of%20'democratic%20backsliding%20in%20the%20academia'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A60%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fauthor-of-paper-on-possible-manipulation-in-2019-polls-quits-ashoka-university%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20North%20Florida%20congressional%20district%20that%20was%20held%20by%20a%20Black%20Democrat%20before%20it%20was%20dism