LinkedIn%20said%20they%20had%20planned%20a%20vacation%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuxury%20retail%20client%20advisor%20Razonie%20Napier%20told%20Insider%20that%20he%20struggles%20with%20turning%20off%20his%20work%20phone%20when%20he's%20on%20vacation.%20The%2025-year-old%20said%20he%20often%20overthinks%20while%20he's%20away%20from%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20my%20industry%2C%20I%20do%20feel%20obligated%20to%20be%20available%20to%20my%20clients%2C%26quot%3B%20Napier%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20expect%20me%20to%20be%20there%20for%20them%20if%20they%20need%20an%20item%2C%20and%20I%20have%20to%20because%20it's%20my%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20he%20loves%20his%20job%20helping%20clients%20find%20the%20right%20style%2C%20and%20he%20doesn't%20mind%20answering%20their%20calls%20when%20he's%20not%20at%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-guilty-vacation-boomers-millenials-gen-x-linkedin-survey-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691954181000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d91b6e1f51cc00196884db%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-guilty-vacation-boomers-millenials-gen-x-linkedin-survey-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20third%20of%20Gen%20Z%20professionals%20feel%20obliged%20to%20work%20during%20vacation%2C%20says%20LinkedIn%20study.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jhart%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Hart)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A119%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-guilty-vacation-boomers-millenials-gen-x-linkedin-survey-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Locarno%20Emerging%20Director%20Winner%20Katharina%20Huber%20Breaks%C2%A0Down%20%E2%80%98A%20Good%20Place%E2%80%99%3A%20%E2%80%98Progress%20Can%20Sometimes%20Be%20Reactionary%E2%80%99%22%2C%2