p%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20so%2C%20there%20is%20the%20overriding%20argument%20we%20hear%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Clive%20amongst%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eyour%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20folks.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20you%20are%20a%20Hindu%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20live%20in%20an%20area%20dominated%20by%20or%20surrounded%20by%20Muslims%2C%20and%20vice%20versa.%20And%20because%20you%20never%20know%20if%20and%20when%20any%20such%20a%20moment%20will%20come%20in%20your%20life%2C%20you%20tend%20to%20follow%20your%20fears.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%2C%20%E2%80%9Conly%20Hindus%20can%20protect%20Hindus%20and%20only%20Muslims%20can%20protect%20Muslims%E2%80%9D%20is%20the%20overriding%20argument%20in%20the%20India%20of%20the%2021st%20century.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuch%20%E2%80%98facts%E2%80%99%20and%20such%20%E2%80%98arguments%E2%80%99%20go%20hand%20in%20hand%2C%20traversing%20the%20length%20and%20breadth%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20past%2070-odd%20years%2C%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20appear%20to%20have%20increasingly%20followed%20this%20undeclared%20dictum.%20With%20rapid%20urbanisation%2C%20rural%20and%20small%20town%20populations%20have%20shifted%20base.%20Big%20and%20small%20cities%20have%20mushroomed%20rapidly%20in%20the%20Indian%20landscape.%20In%20such%20cities%2C%20everybody%20has%2C%20first%20and%20foremost%2C%20a%20desire%20to%20get%20a%20good%20job%2C%20set%20up%20a%20good%20business%2C%20get%20a%20good%20education%2C%20have%20access%20to%20good%20medical%20facilities%2C%20and%20all%20the%20other%20material%20goods%20one%20can%20think%20of.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EValid%20aspirations%2C%20aren%E2%80%99t%20they%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EUrban%20versus%20Rural%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThose%20living%20in%20villages%20may%20have%20the%20same%20aspirations.%20They%2C%20too%2C%20may%20be%20longing%20for%20a%20good%20life%20within%20the%20limited%20and%20available%20resources%20they%20have.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20unlike%20the%20neo-urban%20population%2C%20their%20preferences%20and%20priorities%20are%20different.%20Perhaps%20their%20overarching%20desire%20is%20to%20have%20good%20neighbours%20and%20live%20in%20a%20close-knit%20society.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fghettoisation-muslims-mental-health%2F%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20Ghettoisation%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Muslims%20Adversely%20Affects%20their%20Mental%20Health%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20places%20that%20are%20not%20urban%2C%20civic%20facilities%20are%20scarce.%20So%20in%20an%20emergency%2C%20those%20who%20live%20there%20need%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20moral%20and%20physical%20support.%20It%20could%20be%20said%20that%20religious%20identity%20is%20secondary%20to%20them.%20Religion%20itself%20is%20rather%20simple%20and%20resides%20deep%20in%20their%20faith%20system.%20Of%20course%2C%20it%20would%20be%20na%C3%AFve%20to%20say%20that%20there%20is%20no%20religious%20divide%20in%20the%20villages%20and%20small%20towns%20of%20India.%20Religious%20identities%20result%20in%20cultural%20differences%20as%20well%2C%20but%2C%20in%20my%20view%2C%20they%20are%20mostly%20confined%20to%20the%20domestic%20and%20private%20arena.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20over-assertion%20of%20rituals%20and%20religious%20festivities%20by%20one%20community%20or%20the%20other%20can%20sometimes%20lead%20to%20skirmishes%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20has%20been%20known%20to%20lead%20to%20communal%20riots.%20But%20once%20the%20dust%20settles%2C%20both%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%2C%20irrespective%20of%20whose%20population%20is%20more%20in%20a%20particular%20area%2C%20seem%20to%20reconcile%20and%20go%20on%20co-existing.%20They%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20shift%20their%20homes%20or%20fields%20to%20%E2%80%98safer%E2%80%99%20places%2C%20unlike%20how%20urban%20people%20seem%20to%20be%20able%20to%20do.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20so%2C%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20are%20villages%20and%20towns%20entirely%20or%20predominantly%20inhabited%20by%20one%20community%20or%20the%20other%2C%20there%20is%20no%20ghetto.%20A%20line%20of%20division%20may%20be%20there%2C%20but%20that%20is%20often%20largely%20invisible.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20urban%20settings%2C%20though%2C%20the%20picture%20is%20strikingly%20different.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20urban%20phenomenon%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBecause%20the%20urbanites%20are%20mostly%2C%20if%20not%20all%2C%20displaced%20people%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20archetypal%20memory%20or%20attachment%20to%20their%20new%20abodes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBecause%20they%20are%20keen%20to%20earn%20according%20to%20their%20aspirations%20and%20can%20secure%20access%20to%20most%20facilities%20on%20their%20own%2C%20without%20seeking%20the%20help%20of%20a%20neighbour%2C%20they%20feel%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20require%20the%20community%20life%20they%20found%20necessary%20in%20villages.%20Inter-dependence%2C%20which%20is%20central%20to%20village%20residents%E2%80%99%20harmony%20with%20each%20other%2C%20has%20little%20meaning%20in%20urban%20settings.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%20the%20urbanites%E2%80%99%20sense%20of%20community%20can%20appear%20far%20stronger%2C%20even%20vocal%20at%20times%20and%20more%20aggressive.%20Religion%20here%20is%20not%20simple.%20It%20is%20strong%20and%20evocative.%20It%20dominates%20life%2C%20but%20for%20no%20reasons%20apparent%20outwardly%2C%20with%20no%20visible%20signs%2C%20can%20suddenly%20surface.%20The%20books%20interpreting%20religious%20scriptures%20are%2C%20at%20one%20end%2C%20soft%20like%20a%20cotton%20ball%20and%20at%20the%20other%20end%2C%20sharp%20and%20unbending%20like%20a%20dagger.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20prosperity%20promised%20and%20ambitions%20high%2C%20elements%20of%20spirituality%20and%20contentment%20which%20are%20understood%20to%20be%20the%20core%20of%20religion%2C%20bear%20little%20relevance%20in%20an%20urban%20population%E2%80%99s%20life.%20Yet%20their%20sense%20of%20religious%20identity%20remains%20all%20pervading.%20There%20is%20a%20conundrum%20here%3A%20religion%20in%20them%20appears%20skin-deep%20and%20yet%2C%20religious%20identity%20is%20writ%20large%20on%20their%20face.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20Hindu%2C%20whether%20or%20not%20s(he)%20is%20religious%20and%20a%20Muslim%2C%20whether%20or%20not%20s(he)%20is%20a%20practicing%20one%2C%20have%20access%20to%20big%20mosques%20and%20grand%20temples.%20They%20have%20community%20leaders%20and%20protectors%20of%20their%20%E2%80%98interests%E2%80%99.%20And%20of%20course%2C%20there%20are%20communal%20conflicts.%20Not%20necessarily%20in%20their%20neighbourhood%2C%20not%20necessarily%20where%20they%20could%20be%20affected%2C%20and%20maybe%20at%20a%20much%20farther%20place%2C%20which%20they%20may%20not%20have%20even%20heard%20of%20before.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20impact%20of%20all%20this%20is%20nearly%20the%20same.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAny%20such%20strife%20is%20enough%20to%20bring%20a%20sense%20of%20insecurity%20in%20them%20and%20they%20think%20of%20shifting%20to%20a%20%E2%80%98secured%E2%80%99%20place%2C%20thus%20creating%20more%20and%20more%20ghettos%2C%20which%20continue%20to%20expand%20even%20in%20times%20of%20peace.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20this%20is%20not%20limited%20to%20less%20well-off%20Muslims.%20Posh%20colonies%2C%20localities%20or%20apartments%20are%20largely%20beyond%20the%20economic%20reach%20of%20most%20members%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20Still%2C%20there%20are%20many%20who%20wish%20to%20live%20a%20quality%20life%20and%20have%20enough%20money%20for%20such%20a%20life%20to%20sustain.%20But%20it%20is%20not%20as%20simple%20for%20them.%20There%20have%20been%20numerous%20instances%20when%20Residents%E2%80%99%20Welfare%20Associations%20have%20resisted%2C%20mostly%20successfully%2C%20attempts%20by%20any%20Muslim%20to%20purchase%20a%20house%20within%20%E2%80%98their%E2%80%99%20area.%20Even%20when%20not%20a%20single%20Muslim%20family%20stays%20there%2C%20an%20unseen%2C%20undeclared%20and%20sub-delicate%20hatred%20towards%20Muslims%20hangs%20like%20a%20dark%20cloud%2C%20overhead.%20So%2C%20effectively%2C%20that%20too%20is%20another%20form%20of%20a%20ghetto.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20another%20aspect%20to%20this%2C%20which%20one%20can%20call%20a%20%E2%80%98wilful%20exodus%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20ever%2C%20in%20any%20posh%20colony%20or%20%E2%80%98good%E2%80%99%20apartment%2C%20the%20population%20of%20educated%20and%20socially%20well-placed%20Muslims%20grows%2C%20a%20sense%20of%20having%20been%20%E2%80%98overtaken%E2%80%99%20starts%20pervading%20the%20Hindu%20residents%20there.%20And%20what%20do%20they%20do%2C%20consequently%3F%C2%A0%20They%20start%20shifting%20from%20there%20to%20a%20place%20where%20there%20are%20no%20Muslims%20as%20yet.%20There%2C%20they%20feel%20%E2%80%98secure%E2%80%99.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20standalone%20fact%3B%20this%20is%20a%20phenomenon%20which%20is%20usually%20brushed%20under%20the%20carpet.%20The%20same%20is%20the%20case%20with%20Muslims%2C%20though%20they%20are%20fewer%20in%20number%2C%20compared%20to%20Hindus.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fjuhapura-ahmedabad-ghetto-muslims%5C%22%3EInside%20Ahmedabad%E2%80%99s%20Juhapura%3A%20What%20It%E2%80%99s%20Like%20for%20Muslims%20to%20Live%20in%20a%20Ghetto%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20effective%20result%20in%20both%20cases%20is%20the%20proliferation%20of%20ghettos.%20Muslims%20feel%20secure%20living%20with%20their%20brethren%2C%20Hindus%20with%20their%20folks.%20And%20this%20is%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20both%20need%20to%20deal%20with%20each%20other%20in%20businesses%2C%20in%20services%2C%20and%20in%20workplaces.%20In%20the%20economic%20spheres%20of%20life%2C%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20still%20are%20dependent%20on%20each%20other.%20And%20why%20won%E2%80%99t%20they%20be%3F%20They%20largely%20belong%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20the%20same%20people%2C%20speak%20the%20same%20language%2C%20eat%20the%20same%20foodgrain%20and%20suffer%20or%20enjoy%20the%20same%20weather%20and%20air.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuslims%20go%20to%20hospitals%20where%20they%20are%20treated%20by%20doctors%2C%20who%20may%20be%20Hindus.%20And%20Hindus%20go%20to%20Muslims%E2%80%99%20restaurants%20to%20savour%20delicious%20biryani%2C%20kebabs%20and%20Mughlai%20dishes.%20Children%20go%20to%20schools%2C%20older%20ones%20go%20to%20colleges%20and%20universities%20and%20make%20friends%20with%20each%20other%2C%20without%20letting%20their%20religious%20identities%20come%20in%20between.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20yet%20they%20live%2C%20out%20of%20an%20unseen%20and%20ever-lingering%20fear%20and%20mistrust%2C%20in%20separate%20and%20clearly%20demarcated%20areas.%20Their%20ghettos.%20Back%20in%20their%20ghettos%2C%20this%20liberalism%2C%20secularism%20and%20brotherhood%20vanishes.%20Because%20there%2C%20the%20air%20is%20thick%20with%20the%20purported%20injustices%20meted%20out%20to%20the%20Muslims%20or%20the%20imaginary%20fear%20of%20Muslims%20outnumbering%20Hindus.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20most%20of%20them%20speak%20the%20same%20language%20of%20victimhood%20and%20portray%20the%20same%20mistrust%20towards%20the%20other.%20They%20have%20grown%20up%20with%20this%20notion%20and%20their%20children%20also%20grow%20up%20with%20the%20same%20notion%20of%20otherness.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20educated%20and%20affluent%20class%2C%20which%20is%20less%20prone%20to%20be%20affected%20by%20communal%20strife%20is%20rather%20more%20radicalised%2C%20exudes%20more%20mistrust%20and%20is%20filled%20with%20more%20hatred.%20Effectively%2C%20both%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20in%20large%20urban%20swathes%20of%20India%20are%20happy%20in%20their%20ghettos%20and%20this%20alienation%20is%20increasing%20day%20by%20day.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20extend%20their%20trust%20towards%20each%20other%2C%20thus%20depriving%20their%20children%20of%20a%20composite%20and%20humane%20culture.%20Mixed%20populations%20which%20were%20not%20uncommon%20in%20urban%20areas%20once%2C%20are%20fast%20becoming%20a%20rarity%20in%20semi-urban%20towns%2C%20along%20with%20big%20and%20small%20cities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20most%20unfortunate%20fact%20is%20that%20the%20educated%20and%20financially%20well-off%20middle-class%20Muslims%20and%20Hindus%2C%20who%20are%20safer%20than%20people%20living%20in%20unorganised%2C%20unplanned%20or%20undeveloped%20areas%20or%20localities%2C%20are%20not%20keen%20to%20beat%20ghettoisation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20is%20worrying%20is%20that%20if%20it%20continues%20this%20way%2C%20India%2C%20as%20a%20composite%20society%2C%20will%20suffer%20immense%20losses.%20The%20urbanites%20are%2C%20wittingly%20or%20unwittingly%2C%20making%20the%20task%20easier%20for%20those%20who%20are%20out%20to%20sharply%20divide%20the%20country%20in%20the%20name%20of%20making%20an%20undivided%20India%20or%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eakhand%20bharat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20big%20question%20is%2C%20is%20there%20a%20way%20out%3F%20It%20gets%20harder%20everyday%20with%20the%20kind%20of%20blatantly%20divisive%20social%20atmosphere%20which%20is%20promoted%20by%20the%20powers%20that%20be.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp