r%20also%20served%20the%20purpose%20of%20soaking%20up%20the%20sweat%20that%20broke%20out%20when%20I%20started%20slugging%20vodka%20or%20flavored%20rum%20right%20after%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%2C%20living%20in%20my%20own%20apartment%20on%2084th%20and%202nd%20Avenue%2C%20I%20went%20to%20AA%20meetings%20almost%20every%20night%20on%20the%20Upper%20East%20Side.%20Because%20I%20didn't%20have%20time%20to%20go%20home%20between%20work%20and%20meetings%2C%20and%20I%20couldn't%20bear%20the%20thought%20of%20not%20dressing%20as%20a%20girl%20after%20having%20been%20in%20a%20straitjacket%20of%20a%20suit%20all%20day%2C%20there%20was%20only%20one%20answer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20spent%20the%20day%20as%20Clark%20Kent%20and%20on%20the%20way%20out%20of%20Goldman%20Sachs%20I%20transformed%20into%20Wonder%20Woman%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20day%20in%20late%20November%2C%20I%20began%20to%20get%20squirrelly%20around%205%20p.m.%20just%20like%20when%20I%20was%20drinking%2C%20but%20instead%20of%20vodka%20I%20needed%20lipstick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Maeve%20DuVally%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d676ba5e5d5a00195c82c8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22721%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMaeve%20DuVally%20running%20in%20the%20Atacama%20Desert%20before%20transitioning%20from%20male%20to%20female.%3Cp%3EMaeve%20DuVally%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20left%20the%20privacy%20of%20my%20office%2C%20I%20applied%20eye%20shadow%2C%20mascara%2C%20and%20brow%20definer.%20Looking%20at%20myself%20in%20that%20small%2C%20pink%20hand%20mirror%2C%20I%20felt%20I%20had%20struck%20the%20right%20balance%3A%20I%20was%20already%20feeling%20better%20because%20I%20had%20begun%20to%20transform%2C%20but%20not%20enough%20for%20anybody%20to%20really%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20assistants%20tapped%20on%20the%20glass%20window%20of%20my%20office.%20I%20hurriedly%20pushed%20all%20my%20makeup%20into%20my%20top%20drawer%2C%20stood%20up%20and%20opened%20the%20door.%20%26quot%3BDo%20you%20want%20to%20take%20a%20call%20from%20Bloomberg%3F%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20answered%2C%20wondering%20if%20she%20had%20noticed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20could%20have%20sworn%20she%20looked%20at%20me%20funny%2C%20but%20I%20couldn't%20be%20sure%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20call%2C%20I%20went%20to%20the%20men's%20room%2C%20where%20I%20changed%20into%20pink%20corduroy%20pants%2C%20a%20bra%2C%20a%20pink%20sweater%2C%20and%20black%20high-heeled%20boots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20going%20through%20my%20email%20one%20last%20time%2C%20I%20carefully%20packed%20my%20belongings%2C%20keeping%20accessible%20what%20I%20needed%20for%20the%20final%20touches%20to%20my%20appearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221688%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Maeve%20DuVally%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d67aa45e5d5a00195c88e3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222588%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDuVally's%20book%20cover.%3Cp%3EMaeve%20DuVally%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EObviously%2C%20minimizing%20my%20time%20transforming%20in%20the%20men's%20rooms%20decreased%20the%20likelihood%20that%20somebody%20would%20walk%20in%20on%20me.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20office%20had%20cleared%20out%20early%20so%20I%20did%20something%20I%20didn't%20normally%20do%20on%20my%20floor%3A%20I%20put%20a%20light%20coating%20of%20deep%20red%20lip-%20stick%20on%20and%20headed%20for%20the%20elevator.%20A%20slow-to-come%20elevator%20used%20to%20enrage%20me%20when%20I%20couldn't%20get%20out%20of%20the%20building%20fast%20enough%20to%20get%20some%20liquor%20in%20me.%20It%20was%20almost%20as%20bad%20today%20because%20I%20stood%20exposed%20in%20the%20hallway%20with%20lipstick%20on%20and%20no%20place%20to%20retreat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20elevator%20came%20and%20I%20rushed%20in.%20Good%2C%20I%20said%20to%20myself%2C%20only%20one%20other%20person%20was%20present.%20Feeling%20relatively%20safe%2C%20I%20dutifully%20took%20out%20my%20iPhone%20because%20that's%20what%20people%20do%20on%20elevators.%20Peeking%20up%20at%20the%20other%20occupant%2C%20I%20realized%20he%20was%20a%20senior%20investment%20banker%20whom%20I%20had%20been%20friendly%20with.%20We%20often%20talked%20about%20career%20and%20family%20while%20going%20up%20to%20Bloomberg%20for%20TV%20hits.%20Since%20we%20both%20had%20experience%20living%20in%20Asia%2C%20we%20also%20swapped%20stories%20about%20our%20adventures%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20wouldn't%20look%20at%20me%20and%20I%20did%20not%20know%20if%20that%20was%20because%20he%20was%20just%20busy%20answering%20emails%20or%20he%20thought%20I%20was%20some%20type%20of%20freak%20with%20makeup%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cem%3EWhat's%20he%20thinking%3F%20Why%20is%20he%20ignoring%20me%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESuddenly%20the%20grains%20on%20the%20tan%20ligneous%20walls%20of%20the%20elevator%20began%20twisting%20and%20the%20car%20started%20getting%20smaller%20and%20smaller.%20I%20really%20needed%20to%20get%20out%20immediately.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20door%20slid%20open%2C%20I%20sprinted%20out%20to%20the%20second%20elevator%20I%20had%20to%20take%20down%20to%20the%20first%20floor.%20This%20one%20was%20larger%20and%20always%20full%2C%20so%20it%20was%20easier%20to%20sink%20into%20the%20corner%20and%20be%20anonymous.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20thick%20wooden%20stalls%20and%20higher%20quality%20marble%2C%20the%20bathroom%20on%20the%20first%20floor%20of%20Goldman%20Sachs'%20headquarters%20was%20grander%20than%20others%20in%20the%20building%20because%20client%20events%20were%20often%20held%20on%20the%20first%20floor.%20This%20bathroom%2C%20the%20closest%20to%20the%20exits%2C%20was%20rarely%20occupied%20at%20six%20or%20seven%2C%20when%20I%20was%20leaving.%20I%20put%20on%20my%20wig%2C%20added%20to%20my%20makeup%20and%20donned%20a%20frilled%20yellow%20blouse.