e.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fnation%2Fnext-round-of-talks-over-lac-stand-off-tomorrow-534630%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3ETribune%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20talks%20have%20been%20scheduled%20after%20almost%20four%20months.%20The%20last%20round%20was%20conducted%20on%20April%2023.%20It%2C%20however%2C%20ended%20in%20a%20stalemate.%20Since%20then%20there%20has%20been%20a%20series%20of%20high-level%20contacts%20between%20the%20two%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20delegation%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20headed%20by%20Lt%20Gen%20Rashim%20Bali%2C%20Commander%20of%20the%20Leh-headquartered%2014%20Corps.%20The%20Chinese%20team%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20led%20by%20the%20commander%20of%20the%20South%20Xinjiang%20Military%20District%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20delegation%20at%20the%20talks%20is%20going%20to%20seek%20completion%20of%20the%20disengagement%20process%20in%20the%20remaining%20friction%20points%20at%20the%20earliest%2C%20said%20one%20of%20the%20persons%20cited%20above%2C%20one%20of%20the%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20told%20PTI%20on%20Saturday%2C%20August%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%2018th%20round%20of%20talks%2C%20held%20on%20April%2023%2C%20the%20Indian%20side%20had%20strongly%20pressed%20for%20resolving%20the%20lingering%20issues%20at%20Depsang%20and%20Demchok.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691924428000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2Findia-china-flags-pti-crop.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Findia-china-military-commander-talks-on-lac-standoff-to-be-held-on-august-14%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20would%20be%20the%2019th%20round%20of%20talks%20since%20June%202020.%20The%20talks%20are%20said%20to%20take%20place%20at%20the%20Chushul-Moldo%20border%20meeting%20point%20on%20the%20Indian%20side.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Findia-china-military-commander-talks-on-lac-standoff-to-be-held-on-august-14%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20the%20World%20Discovered%20%E2%80%93%20and%20Got%20the%20Taste%20for%20%E2%80%93%20Scotch%20Whiskey%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13162422%2F14179521094_2c1b5c942a_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EScotch%20whiskey%20exports%20grew%20from%20%C2%A34.51%20billion%20in%202021%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scotch-whisky.org.uk%2Fnewsroom%2Fscotch-whisky-exports-2022%2F%5C%22%3Eto%20more%20than%20%C2%A36%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022%2C%20while%20separate%20government%20figures%20showed%20a%2025%25%20sales%20increase%20last%20year%20%E2%80%93%20the%20biggest%20for%20any%20UK%20manufactured%20product%20except%20aircraft%20parts.%20Such%20impressive%20growth%20shows%20how%20the%20industry%20has%20cultivated%20its%20image%2C%20appeal%20and%20supply%20networks%20over%20200%20years%2C%20withstanding%20pandemics%2C%20trade%20wars%20and%20even%20world%20wars%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20of%20why%20Scotch%20whiskey%20has%20managed%20to%20keep%20its%20global%20popularity%20over%20a%20long%20time%20period%20is%20one%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gla.ac.uk%2Fschools%2Fbusiness%2Fstaff%2Fniallmackenzie%2F%23publications%2Cbooksections%5C%22%3Eresearching%20for%20several%20years%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Like%20a%20good%20Scotch%2C%20the%20answer%20is%20complex%20and%20requires%20time%20to%20understand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScotch%20whiskey%20producers%20have%20long%20looked%20overseas%20to%20sell%20their%20product.%20The%20UK%20domestic%20market%20is%20not%20and%20never%20has%20been%20big%20enough%20to%20meet%20their%20aspirations%20for%20growth.%20Some%20of%20the%20earliest%20records%20of%20Scotch%20being%20exported%20date%20to%201839%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ardbegproject.com%2Fardbeg-in-usa.shtml%5C%22%3Eadverts%20for%20Ardbeg%20Scotch%20from%20Islay%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20others%20appearing%20in%20New%20York%20publications%20around%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20was%20not%20until%20later%20in%20the%2019th%20century%20that%20the%20Scotch%20whiskey%20industry%20really%20began%20to%20focus%20on%20going%20global.%20In%20the%20mid%201800s%2C%20the%20government%20relaxed%20regulations%20regarding%20blending.%20Previously%20producers%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20mix%20or%20blend%20their%20individual%20whiskies%2C%20which%20were%20often%20raw%20and%20inconsistent.%20After%20the%20rules%20changed%2C%20the%20industry%20could%20produce%20a%20consistent%20and%20wide%20variety%20of%20flavours%20to%20suit%20different%20palates%2C%20giving%20whiskey%20the%20opportunity%20to%20appeal%20more%20broadly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECombined%20with%20already%20established%20global%20trade%20routes%20out%20of%20the%20UK%2C%20Scotch%20whiskey%20blenders%20such%20as%20Dewar%E2%80%99s%2C%20Buchanan%E2%80%99s%20and%20Johnnie%20Walker%20were%20able%20to%20grow%20their%20businesses%20domestically%20and%20overseas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20global%20taste%20for%20whiskey%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20blended%20Scotch%20whiskey%20makes%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scotch-whisky.org.uk%2Fnewsroom%2Fscotch-whisky-exports-2022%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20majority%20(59%25)%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20industry%E2%80%99s%20exports%20by%20value.%20Blended%20Scotch%20also%20achieved%20the%20biggest%20increase%20in%20exports%20in%20the%20last%20year.%20It%20grew%20by%2043%25%2C%20fuelling%20the%20overall%20Scotch%20export%20value%20increase%20of%2025%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20India%20and%20China%20have%20emerged%20in%20recent%20years%20as%20key%20destinations%2C%20the%20early%20export%20markets%20established%20by%20Scotch%20producers%20such%20as%20the%20US%2C%20France%2C%20South%20America%2C%20and%20Asian%20countries%20including%20Singapore%20and%20Taiwan%2C%20are%20still%20the%20principal%20destinations%20for%20Scotch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20industry%20has%20been%20subject%20to%20close%20attention%20from%20the%20Westminster%20government%20in%20the%20form%20of%20regulation%20and%20taxation%20for%20the%20past%20200%20years%2C%20starting%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scotch-whisky.org.uk%2Fdiscover%2Fstory-of-scotch%2F%23%3A%257E%3Atext%3DIn%25201823%2520the%2520Excise%2520Act%2Cper%2520gallon%2520of%2520proof%2520spirithave%5C%22%3EExcise%20Act%20of%201823%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20has%20encouraged%20the%20industry%E2%80%99s%20overseas%20focus.%20Tariffs%20and%20outright%20bans%20such%20as%20US%20prohibition%20from%201920-1933%20did%20little%20to%20dampen%20thirst%20for%20the%20spirit.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20prohibition%2C%20the%20industry%20used%20all%20manner%20of%20means%20to%20get%20Scotch%20into%20the%20US%20including%20rum%20runners%20in%20the%20Caribbean%20and%20mobster%20ties%20through%20Canada%20%E2%80%93%20most%20recently%20depicted%20in%20the%20TV%20show%20Peaky%20Blinders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20since%20the%20early%2020th%20century%2C%20the%20UK%20government%20has%20recognised%20and%20pushed%20the%20export%20value%20of%20Scotch%20as%20a%20benefit%20to%20the%20economy.%20Winston%20Churchill%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fmagazines%2Fpanache%2Fwinston-churchills-painting-of-his-favourite-whisky-goes-on-sale-expected-to-fetch-330k%2Farticleshow%2F79147333.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ea%20well-known%20Scotch%20drinker%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20recognised%20its%20dollar-earning%20value%20during%20the%20second%20world%20war%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscotchwhisky.com%2Fmagazine%2Ffamous-whisky-drinkers%2F9866%2Fsir-winston-churchill%2F%5C%22%3Ea%201945%20government%20memo%3C%2Fa%3E%20stating%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20no%20account%20reduce%20the%20barley%20for%20whiskey.%20This%20takes%20years%20to%20mature%20and%20is%20an%20invaluable%20export%20%E2%80%A6%20Having%20regard%20to%20all%20our%20other%20difficulties%20about%20export%2C%20it%20would%20be%20most%20improvident%20not%20to%20preserve%20this%20characteristic%20British%20element%20of%20ascendancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20focus%20on%20exports%20damaged%20the%20domestic%20trade.%20After%20US%20prohibition%20and%20the%20second%20world%20war%2C%20global%20Scotch%20whiskey%20exports%20grew%20as%20a%20proportion%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F00076791.2022.2085251%5C%22%3Efrom%2050%25%20of%20total%20UK%20production%20in%201939%20to%2075%25%20by%201954%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20industry%20has%20since%20faced%20various%20challenges%20in%20international%20markets%2C%20but%20has%20still%20continued%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERising%20to%20the%20challenge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScotch%20exports%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-scotland-scotland-business-36302482%5C%22%3Eslower%20in%20recent%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20the%20combined%20effects%20of%20free%20movement%20(affecting%20the%20important%20duty-free%20market%20for%20Scotch)%20and%20trade%20restrictions%20arising%20from%20the%20global%20pandemic%2C%20Brexit%20and%20the%20introduction%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedrinksbusiness.com%2F2023%2F07%2Findia-reconsiders-tariffs-on-imports-of-bulk-whisky%2F%5C%22%3Ehigh%20tariffs%20in%20key%20markets%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20as%20the%20US%20and%20India.%20But%20whiskey%20producers%20have%20clearly%20learned%20lessons%20from%20a%20long%20history%20of%20responding%20to%20global%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20industry%20quickly%20adapted%20by%20focusing%20on%20quality%20and%20luxury%20and%20pushing%20new%20products.%20The%20emergence%20of%20single%20malts%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F00076791.2022.2085251%5C%22%3Eover%20the%20past%2030%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20distinct%20product%20in%20export%20markets%20is%20a%20good%20example%20of%20this.%20Prior%20to%20the%20early%201990s%2C%20single%20malt%20was%20a%20relatively%20niche%20product%20without%20significant%20reach%20into%20markets%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F00076791.2022.2085251%5C%22%3Eeither%20at%20home%20or%20abroad%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Then%2C%20a%20global%20collapse%20in%20demand%20for%20blended%20Scotch%20led%20to%20an%20overstocking%20of%20single%20malt%20%E2%80%9Cfillings%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20the%20ingredients%20for%20blended%20Scotch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20industry%20used%20marketing%2C%20branding%20and%20distribution%20strategies%20to%20turn%20this%20overstock%20into%20a%20luxury%20product%20by%20building%20the%20perception%20of%20scarcity%2C%20and%20value%20in%20age%20and%20provenance.%20Single%20malts%20have%20since%20grown%20to%20comprise%20around%20a%20quarter%20of%20the%20value%20of%20Scotch%20exports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20the%20Scotch%20whiskey%20industry%E2%80%99s%20recent%20success%20in%20export%20growth%20did%20not%20happen%20overnight.%20It%20has%20taken%20a%20long%20time%20to%20develop%20and%20mature.%20Much%20like%20a%20good%20Scotch%20whiskey.%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Conversation%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcounter.theconversation.com%2Fcontent%2F210595%2Fcount.gif%3Fdistributor%3Drepublish-lightbox-basic%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENiall%20G%20MacKenzie%2C%20Professor%20of%20Entrepreneurship%20and%20Business%20History%2C%20University%20of%20Glasgow.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20republished%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%5C%22%3EThe%20Conversation%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20a%20Creative%20Commons%20license.%20Read%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fhow-canny-marketing-and-strong-supply-links-gave-the-world-a-taste-for-scotch-whisky-210595%5C%22%3Eoriginal%20article%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691924184000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13162422%2F14179521094_2c1b5c942a_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffood%2Fhow-the-world-discovered-and-got-the-taste-for-scotch-whiskey%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Like%20a%20good%20Scotch%2C%20the%20answer%20is%20complex%20and%20requires%20time%20to%20understand.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffood%2Fhow-the-world-discovered-and-got-the-taste-for-scotch-whiskey%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Ahead%20of%20Polls%2C%20PM%20Modi%20Pitches%20Ravidas%20Against%20Mughals%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13160642%2FScreenshot-2023-08-13-at-4.06.29-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20August%2012%20remembered%20medieval-era%20Bhakti%20poet%20Sant%20Ravidas%20for%20his%20%E2%80%9Ccourage%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cpatriotism%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhow-the-ichr-is-inventing-history-under-the-modi-government%5C%22%3Eduring%20the%20Mughal%20period%20when%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20Modi%2C%20Indian%20society%20grappled%20with%20%E2%80%9Cassaults%20on%20its%20faith%E2%80%9D%20and%20attempts%20to%20%E2%80%9Cerase%20its%20identity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20made%20the%20remarks%20after%20launching%20several%20projects%20in%20poll-bound%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20It%20included%20him%20laying%20the%20foundation%20stone%20of%20a%20memorial%20dedicated%20to%20Ravidas%2C%20a%20poet%20and%20philosopher%20who%20stood%20against%20institutionalised%20caste%20hierarchy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20performed%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebhoomi%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Epujan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(rituals%20for%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20grounds)%20for%20the%20Sant%20Shiromani%20Gurudev%20Shri%20Ravidas%20ji%20Memorial%20at%20an%20event%20in%20Sagar%2C%20a%20district%20located%20in%20the%20Bundelkhand%20region%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavidas%20is%20revered%20by%20a%20large%20number%20of%20Dalits%2C%20especially%20in%20northern%20states%20such%20as%20Punjab%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20The%20Bundelkhand%20region%20of%20MP%2C%20consisting%20of%20seven%20districts%2C%20has%20a%20Dalit%20population%20much%20above%20the%20state%20average%20of%2015.6%25%20(as%20per%20the%202011%20Census).%20Thus%20the%20building%20pf%20memorials%20and%20the%20promotion%20of%20popular%20Dalit%20icons%20has%20over%20the%20years%20emerged%20as%20a%20strategy%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20to%20woo%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Sagar%2C%20which%20has%20a%20Dalit%20population%20of%20over%2021%25%2C%20Modi%20evoked%20a%20popular%20couplet%20of%20Ravidas%20which%20speaks%20against%20the%20idea%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Eparadheenta%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20dependence%20and%20connected%20it%20with%20present%20India%E2%80%99s%20spirit%20of%20rejecting%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmentality%20of%20slavery.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EParadheenta%20paap%20hai%2C%20jaan%20lehu%20re%20meet.%20Raidas%20paradheen%20sau%2C%20kaun%20kare%20hain%20preet%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoughly%20translated%2C%20it%20means%3A%20dependency%20is%20a%20big%20sin%20and%20those%20who%20accept%20it%20and%20do%20not%20take%20a%20stand%20against%20it%20are%20not%20loved%20by%20anybody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM%20started%20by%20describing%20the%20Mughal%20period%20as%20one%20when%20the%20Indian%20society%20faced%20%E2%80%9Cinstability%2C%20persecution%20and%20oppression.%E2%80%9D%20Even%20during%20those%20days%2C%20Modi%20said%2C%20Ravidas%20tried%20to%20awaken%20the%20society%20and%20teach%20it%20how%20to%20fight%20against%20its%20evil%20practices%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20there%20were%20assaults%20on%20our%20faith%2C%20when%20restrictions%20were%20being%20imposed%20on%20us%20to%20erase%20our%20identity%2C%20even%20in%20those%20days%20%E2%80%93%20during%20the%20Mughal-period%20%E2%80%93%20look%20at%20the%20courage%20and%20patriotism%20with%20which%20Ravidas%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%20%5Bthe%20couplet%5D%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20said%20that%20Ravidas%E2%80%99s%20teachings%20had%20provided%20the%20society%20with%20the%20strength%20to%20fight%20oppression%20and%20that%20even%20Maratha%20ruler%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20had%20used%20it%20as%20an%20inspiration%20to%20lay%20the%20foundation%20of%20%E2%80%9CHindavi%20Swarajya%E2%80%9D%20or%20self-rule%20of%20Indian%20people.%20The%20spirit%20continued%20to%20flow%20through%20the%20efforts%20of%20lakhs%20of%20freedom%20fighters%20during%20the%201857%20struggle%20against%20the%20British%20and%20today%2C%20the%20nation%20was%20moving%20forward%20%E2%80%9Cwith%20the%20same%20spirit%20of%20liberation%20and%20rejecting%20the%20mentality%20of%20slavery%2C%E2%80%9D%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20event%2C%20Modi%20elaborated%20on%20some%20schemes%20that%20had%20benefitted%20people%20from%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20and%20Other%20Backward%20Class%20communities.%E2%80%9D%20These%20groups%20have%20been%20the%20biggest%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20welfare%20schemes%20run%20by%20the%20government%20for%20the%20poor%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202018%20assembly%20election%2C%20the%20Congress%20secured%20more%20seats%20than%20the%20BJP%20and%20managed%20to%20form%20a%20government%20in%20the%20state%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20four%20independent%20winners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%202020%2C%20the%20BJP%20led%20by%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%2C%20toppled%20the%20Kamal%20Nath%20government%20after%20almost%20two%20dozen%20Congress%20MLAs%20resigned%20and%20shifted%20loyalty%20to%20the%20saffron%20party.%20Barring%20the%20one-year%20stint%20of%20Kamal%20Nath%20in%20between%2C%20Chouhan%20has%20been%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20the%20state%20for%20almost%20last%2017%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20the%20BJP%20and%20Chouhan%20are%20battling%20fatigue%20and%20possible%20anti-incumbency%2C%20the%20saffron%20party%20would%20need%20to%20perform%20reasonably%20better%20in%20regions%20such%20as%20Bundelkhand%20where%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20two%20Uttar%20Pradesh-based%20parties%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20had%20a%20decent%20run%20in%20the%20last%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ravidas%20memorial%20would%20be%20constructed%20in%20an%20area%20of%20more%20than%2011.25%20acres%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%20100%20crore.%20It%20will%20include%20an%20art%20museum%20and%20a%20gallery%20to%20showcase%20his%20life%2C%20philosophy%20and%20teachings.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691923466000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13160642%2FScreenshot-2023-08-13-at-4.06.29-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fmadhya-pradesh-election-sagar-narendra-modi-ravidas-mughals%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20poet%20and%20philosopher%20had%20been%20against%20institutionalised%20caste%20hierarchy.%20In%20Sagar%2C%20which%20has%20a%20Dalit%20population%20of%20over%2021%25%2C%20Modi's%20invocation%20of%20Ravidas%20had%20a%20clear%20purpose.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A31%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fmadhya-pradesh-election-sagar-narendra-modi-ravidas-mughals%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lokayukta%3A%20IAS%20officer%20Reiterates%20Faith%20in%20Law%2C%20%E2%80%98Cleared%20in%20Past%20Cases%2C%20No%20Time%20to%20Keep%20Fighting%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13151919%2Fimage-1221.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20preliminary%20inquiry%2C%20the%20order%20of%20which%20was%20made%20public%20on%20August%202%2C%20the%20Manipur%20Lokayukta%20had%20alleged%20that%20IAS%20officer%20Pame%20Armstrong%20%E2%80%9Cdid%20not%20give%20full%20care%20and%20attention%E2%80%9D%20in%20modifying%20the%20compensation%20award%20dated%20June%2015%2C%202017%2C%20in%20a%20case%20concerning%20a%20railway%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPame%20has%20refuted%20all%20the%20charges%20levelled%20against%20him%20by%20the%20preliminary%20inquiry.%20He%20has%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20notice%20issued%20by%20the%20Lokayukta%20before%20August%2021%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20email%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20he%20explained%20his%20position%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20your%20view%2C%20what%20are%20the%20origins%20of%20this%20fraught%20issue%20over%20land%20acquisition%20in%20Manipur%20for%20the%20Railways%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArmstrong%20Pame%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20When%20the%20land%20acquisition%20process%20at%20Marangjing%20in%20Manipur%20started%20in%202010-11%2C%20there%20was%20absolutely%20no%20interference%20whatsoever%20from%20the%20present%20petitioners%20who%20now%20claim%20that%20the%20entire%20land%20of%20the%20village%20is%20a%20common%20land.%20The%20earlier%20phase%20of%20compensation%20was%20paid%20to%20the%20concerned%20land%20owners.%20If%2C%20as%20per%20the%20claim%20of%20the%20petitioners%2C%20land%20in%20the%20hill%20areas%20of%20Manipur%20is%20a%20common%20village%20property%20and%20that%20there%20is%20no%20individual%20land%20owner%2C%20I%20think%20there%20would%20be%20an%20uproar%20everywhere%20else%20across%20the%20hill%20districts%20of%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20personally%20handled%20compensation%20matters%20in%20the%20area%20of%20Tamenglong%20and%20land%20acquired%20for%20various%20projects%20have%20been%20under%20the%20name%20of%20the%20land%20owners.%20Just%20to%20turn%20it%20in%20their%20favour%2C%20they%20cannot%20suddenly%20change%20the%20land%20holding%20systems%20of%20the%20tribals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20present%20issue%20has%20its%20origins%20in%202014-15%2C%20when%20the%20Railways%20sent%20a%20requirement%20for%20over%20137%20acres%20of%20land%20in%20and%20around%20Makhuam-Kharam%20Pallen-Pungmuon%20villages%20area.%20When%20the%20District%20Collector%20(DC)%20at%20that%20time%20deputed%20the%20concerned%20%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESub%20Divisional%20Officer%3C%2Fspan%3E%20(SDO)%20of%20Tamenglong%20to%20do%20field%20survey%2C%20there%20was%20an%20opposition%2C%20too%2C%20from%20this%20group%20of%20villagers%20led%20by%20Gongchalung%20and%20his%20party%20against%20the%20Pungmoun%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20all%20these%20pressures%20to%20stop%20the%20land%20acquisition%20process%2C%20the%20then%20DC%20sent%20the%20requirements%20of%20this%20land%20to%20the%20Revenue%20Department%2C%20Government%20of%20Manipur%2C%20indicating%20clearly%20under%20whose%20village%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20the%20land%20falls.%20It%20may%20clearly%20be%20seen%20from%20the%20letter%20that%20the%20portion%20of%2037%20acres%20was%20under%20Marangjing%20village%2C%2022%20acres%20disputed%20while%2077%20acres%20was%20under%20the%20Pungmuon%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20follow%20up%20of%20the%20field%20report%2C%20the%20then%20DC%2C%20Ngaranchan%20Luikham%2C%20forwarded%20the%20entire%20evaluation%20along%20with%20financial%20implications%20to%20the%20concerned%20authorities%20along%20with%20the%20field%20survey%20reports%2C%20with%20names%20of%20the%20land%20owner%20in%20the%20case%20of%2037%20and%2077%20acres%20while%20that%20of%2022%20acres%20as%20disputed.%20It%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20compensation%20amount%20for%2022%20acres%2C%20which%20has%20been%20recorded%20as%20disputed%2C%20still%20is%20not%20awarded%20to%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20would%20not%20like%20to%20go%20into%20the%20process%20of%20the%20land%20acquisition%20because%20this%20would%20mean%20undermining%20the%20acts%20of%20former%20DCs%20who%2C%20in%20all%20their%20wisdom%2C%20had%20carried%20out%20the%20entire%20process%20judiciously%20following%20all%20laid%20down%20rules%20and%20procedures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Marangjing%20village%20had%20the%20habit%20of%20taking%20law%20and%20order%20in%20their%20own%20hands%20by%20burning%20down%20vehicles%20and%20machinery%20if%20anything%20goes%20against%20their%20favour.%20When%20they%20lost%20the%20case%20on%20June%2016%2C%202017%2C%20it%20was%20the%20same%3B%20things%20went%20out%20of%20control%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20damage%20of%20several%20properties%20of%20both%20public%20and%20private%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maringjing%20village%20being%20a%20big%20village%20always%20wants%20to%20superimpose%20their%20authority%20over%20smaller%20villages%20like%20Pungmoun%2C%20despite%20having%20lost%20almost%20all%20the%20cases%20they%20themselves%20have%20filed.%20At%20any%20given%20instances%2C%20they%20would%20collect%20all%20the%20keys%20to%20the%20machines%20and%20immediately%20halt%20the%20work%20within%20their%20village%20jurisdiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20am%20not%20wrong%2C%20theirs%20is%20the%20only%20village%20which%20had%20expelled%20several%20families%20of%20its%20own%20native%20villagers%20for%20supporting%20the%20order%20of%20the%20district%20administration%20and%20supporting%20the%20Railway%20works%2C%20after%20their%20houses%20being%20totally%20ransacked%20and%20destroyed%20by%20their%20own%20villagers.%20These%20families%20now%20live%20in%20and%20around%20the%20Imphal%20area%20in%20other%20lands%2C%20unable%20to%20come%20back%20and%20settle%20in%20their%20own%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13114421%2Fimage-1215.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22861%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13114421%2Fimage-1215.png%20608w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13114421%2Fimage-1215-300x209.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-667850%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22599%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EHouse%20of%20Mr.%20Gaijinlung%20Kahmei%20%E2%80%93%20one%20of%20the%20land%20owners%20of%20Makhuam%20village%20%E2%80%93%20being%20destroyed%20for%20supporting%20the%20government%20and%20court%E2%80%99s%20verdict.%20He%20has%20since%20been%20expelled%20from%20his%20own%20village%20and%20is%20now%20living%20in%20the%20Imphal%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13114556%2Fimage-1216.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22984%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13114556%2Fimage-1216.png%20781w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13114556%2Fimage-1216-300x160.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-667851%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22524%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ELandowners%20of%20Marangjing%20village%20in%20support%20of%20Railway%20work%20despite%20bandh%20by%20on%20the%20work%20by%20their%20own%20villagers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20complainants%20before%20the%20Manipur%20Lokayukta%20accuse%20you%20of%20having%20%E2%80%98siphoned%20off%E2%80%99%20funds%2C%20what%20is%20your%20position%20on%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArmstrong%20Pame%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20same%20complainants%2C%20having%20lost%20this%20case%20at%20the%20DC%20office%20before%20my%20arrival%2C%20opposed%20the%20survey%20report%20and%20filed%20various%20cases%20in%20both%20the%20Civil%20Judge%20Senior%20Division%20Tamenglong%20and%20the%20District%20Judge%20Imphal%20West.%20According%20to%20the%20Land%20Acquisition%20Act%202013%2C%20the%20District%20Judge%20is%20the%20final%20authority%20for%20reference%20in%20Land%20Acquisition%20Matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20now%20taken%20up%20this%20matter%20with%20the%20Lokayukta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20really%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20many%20more%20courts%20they%20intend%20to%20take%20up%20on%20this%20case.%20One%20thing%20to%20be%20observed%20about%20the%20petitioners%20is%20that%20they%20will%20end%20up%20criticising%20the%20institution%20where%20they%20themselves%20have%20taken%20the%20matter%20for%20justice.%20In%20one%20of%20the%20cases%20which%20they%20lost%20in%20the%20court%20of%C2%A0%20Civil%20Judge%20(Senior%20Division)%20Tamenglong%2C%20they%20had%20even%20accused%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Court%20of%20having%20working%20hand%20in%20glove%20%5Bor%20colluding%5D%20with%20the%20office%20of%20Deputy%20Commissioner%2C%20%5Balleging%5D%20knowing%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20judgement%20beforehand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20one%20of%20the%20complaints%20they%20had%20put%20forth%20in%20the%20Lokayukta%20against%20the%20officer.%20Why%20can%E2%80%99t%20the%20Maranging%20village%20be%20prosecuted%20for%20defaming%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20civil%20court%3F%20If%20they%20have%20no%20faith%20in%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Court%2C%20why%20did%20they%20as%20a%20petitioner%20take%20up%20this%20case%3F%20All%20of%20these%20remain%20to%20be%20answered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20in%20the%20court%20of%20the%20District%20Judge%2C%20Imphal%20West%2C%20they%20were%20the%20petitioners%20and%20lost%20the%20case%20again.%20They%20refused%20to%20accept%20the%20judgment%20as%20it%20went%20against%20their%20favour.%20In%20view%20of%20all%20these%20precedents%2C%20tomorrow%20if%20the%20Lokayukta%20happens%20to%20conclude%20the%20matter%20against%20their%20favour%2C%20I%20would%20not%20be%20surprised%20if%20they%20criticise%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Lokayukta%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%2C%20as%20a%20local%20of%20the%20district%2C%20believe%20in%20the%20best%20coexistence%20between%20the%20two%20villages.%20I%20knew%20that%20going%20through%20legal%20processes%20in%20the%20court%20of%20laws%2C%20enmity%20between%20the%20two%20villages%20would%20only%20be%20enhanced%2C%20and%20the%20amount%20of%20money%20that%20they%20would%20have%20to%20spend%20in%20the%20entire%20legal%20process%20would%20be%20too%20much%20and%20that%20this%20would%20never%20bring%20a%20permanent%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20tried%20to%20reason%20with%20both%20the%20villages%20to%20settle%20the%20matters%20out%20of%20court.%20I%20had%20called%20%5Bthem%5D%20for%20a%20meeting%20in%20my%20office%2C%20discussed%20%5Bthe%20issue%5D%20with%20both%20the%20villages%20separately%20and%20also%20together%20on%20a%20common%20platform.%20However%2C%20I%20was%20unable%20to%20reach%20a%20settlement%20outside%20the%20court%2C%20and%20we%20had%20to%20continue%20with%20the%20legal%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20happened%20on%20June%2014%2C%202017%20in%20my%20Office%20Chamber.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20the%20meeting%2C%20both%20the%20sides%20of%20the%20village%20were%20very%20optimistic%20that%20one%20particular%20case%20(Civil%20Suit%208%20of%202015)%20in%20the%20court%20of%20Civil%20Judge%20Senior%20Division%20Tamenglong%20would%20be%20issued%20in%20their%20respective%20favours.%20They%20had%20not%20mentioned%20any%20other%20case%20apart%20from%20this%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20this%20was%20the%20only%20related%20case%20where%20the%20court%20had%20barred%20the%20DC%E2%80%99s%20office%20from%20awarding%20the%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccordingly%2C%20with%20the%20consensus%20of%20all%20the%20parties%20involved%2C%20the%20award%20was%20modified%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20above%20stated%20order.%20The%20modified%20order%20was%20issued%20on%20June%2015%2C%202017.%20On%20the%20June%2016%2C%20we%20received%20information%20from%20the%20other%20party%2C%20i.e.%20Lovejoy%20of%20Pungmuon%20village%20and%20Thuankunlung%2C%20that%20the%20matter%20had%20been%20dismissed.%20I%20clearly%20had%20told%20them%20that%20without%20a%20hard%20copy%2C%20I%20would%20not%20take%20any%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20some%20time%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20the%20court%20order%20was%20brought%20to%20my%20office%20and%20after%20verifying%20the%20same%2C%20the%20award%20was%20given%20in%20the%20favour%20of%20Thuankulung%20and%20Lovejoy%2C%20as%20per%20all%20available%20records%20in%20the%20office%20as%20reflected%20in%20the%20land%20survey%20records%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20these%20awards%20were%20given%20to%20villagers%20of%20Pungmuon%20village%2C%20through%20Lovejoy%2C%20and%20also%20to%20several%20farmers%20of%20Makhuam%20village%20who%20were%20cultivating%20the%20land%20belonging%20to%20Thuankulung%20of%20Marangjing%20village.%20Both%20of%20them%20had%20produced%20the%20concerned%20documents%20of%20the%20money%20being%20received%20by%20several%20farmers.%20You%20may%20like%20to%20verify%20this%20fact%20by%20going%20through%20all%20the%20APRs%20produced%20at%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20will%20be%20surprised%20that%20the%20same%20petitioners%2C%20who%20were%20leading%20several%20groups%20of%20youths%20and%20some%20women%20from%20the%20village%2C%20went%20on%20a%20rampage%20against%20the%20existing%20properties%2C%20and%20men%20of%20the%20various%20companies%20working%20day%20and%20night%20to%20complete%20the%20railway%20project.%20As%20this%20went%20uncontrollably%2Cto%20bring%20peace%20and%20normalcy%2C%20we%20called%20a%20meeting%20on%20July%205%2C%202017%2C%20and%20agreed%20that%20the%20bank%20accounts%20of%20these%20two%20individuals%20would%20be%20frozen%20till%20the%20time%20whatever%20case%20they%20claimed%20were%20pending%20in%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meeting%20itself%2C%20they%20committed%20to%20give%20up%20all%20protests%20and%20other%20bans%20on%20the%20railway%20works.%20I%20assured%20them%20if%20in%20case%20they%20were%20proven%20right%20in%20the%20court%2C%20all%20the%20recovery%20would%20be%20done%20through%20my%20office.%20For%20the%20next%20eight%20Months%20till%20March%201%2C%202018%2C%20the%20accounts%20remained%20frozen.%20Does%20this%20mean%20I%20was%20scared%20of%20my%20own%20actions%20and%20trying%20to%20protect%20myself%3F%20Absolutely%20not.%20As%20someone%20who%20listens%20to%20their%20prayers%2C%20who%20believes%20in%20the%20law%20of%20the%20land%2C%20waits%20for%20the%20final%20judgment%2C%20I%20acted%20only%20after%20the%20final%20judgment%20was%20given.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20judgment%2C%20paragraph%2023%20reads%2C%20%E2%80%9CSituated%20thus%2C%20I%20come%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%20the%20prayer%20of%20the%20respondent%20no.%204%20to%20direct%20the%20collector%2C%20LA%2C%20Tamenglong%20to%20refer%20his%20claims%20to%20this%20authority%20cannot%20be%20entertained%20as%20there%20is%20no%20failure%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20Collector%2C%20LA%2C%20Tamenglong%20to%20refer%20his%20claim%20to%20the%20authority%20since%20respondent%20No.4%20(Mr.Meithuaniung%20Gangmei%2C%20of%20Makhuam%20Village)%20did%20not%20file%20any%20application%20under%20section%2064(1)%20of%20RFCTLARR%20Act%2C%202013%20and%20that%20he%20has%20also%20failed%20to%20establish%20any%20prima%20facie%20right%20and%20title%20over%20the%20acquired%20lands%20mentioned%20in%20Sl.No.%202%20and%203.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccordingly%2C%20the%20frozen%20accounts%20were%20opened%20again%20after%20receiving%20the%20court%20order.%20Imagine%20if%20I%20had%20not%20unfrozen%20the%20accounts%2C%20I%20would%20have%20faced%20another%20contempt%20of%20court%20from%20the%20other%20party.%20Now%20they%20are%20questioning%20my%20action%20of%20why%20I%20froze%20the%20bank%20account%2C%20despite%20them%20being%20present%20for%20the%20meeting%20and%20agreeing%20on%20this%20already.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20did%20you%20tell%20the%20Lokayukta%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArmstrong%20Pame%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20exactly%20told%20the%20Lokayukta%20that%20no%20wrong%20has%20been%20committed%20on%20my%20part%20and%20that%20I%20had%20followed%20the%20laid%20down%20procedures.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20had%20even%20gone%20beyond%20all%20the%20legal%20provisions%20available%20by%20trying%20to%20bring%20a%20mutual%20understanding%20among%20all%20the%20contesting%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20statement%20has%20been%20furnished%20to%20the%20Lokayukta%20%E2%80%93%20you%20may%20see%20it%20for%20yourself.%20The%20complainant%20party%20makes%20claims%20that%20several%20court%20cases%20are%20still%20pending.%20However%2C%20if%20none%20of%20them%20relates%20to%20the%20award%20matter%2C%20specifically%20forbidding%20the%20District%20Collector%20from%20paying%20the%20compensation%2C%20how%20can%20any%20work%20make%20any%20progress%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20because%20someone%20filed%20a%20case%20today%2C%20and%20even%20without%20the%20court%20order%2C%20does%20it%20mean%20the%20DC%20has%20to%20stop%20working%20in%20anticipation%20of%20the%20unfavourable%20judgment%3F%20Absolutely%20not.%20Do%20you%20think%20any%20land%20acquisition%20would%20have%20happened%20if%20we%20had%20followed%20that%20route%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20should%20at%20least%20have%20the%20confidence%20in%20the%20system%20when%20they%20approach%20for%20justice%2C%20rather%20than%20ridiculing%20it%20when%20the%20judgment%20is%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20maintain%20that%20you%20acted%20as%20per%20court%20orders.%20Then%20why%20did%20the%20Lokayukta%20overlook%20your%20statement%20and%20rule%20in%20the%20preliminary%20inquiry%20as%20it%20did%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArmstrong%20Pame%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Having%20furnished%20all%20my%20statements%2C%20and%20also%20all%20relevant%20annexures%2C%20I%20was%20hoping%20that%20the%20matter%20would%20be%20concluded%20here%20and%20then.%20However%2C%20this%20being%20only%20the%20preliminary%20report%2C%20I%20believe%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Lokayukta%20would%20be%20able%20to%20conclude%20the%20matter%20as%20per%20all%20existing%20documents%20in%20record.%20I%20also%20have%20been%20informed%20that%20Lokayukta%20have%20taken%20all%20files%20available%20in%20the%20office%20of%20DC%20office%2C%20I%20am%20sure%20they%20would%20understand%20the%20entire%20proceeding%20of%20the%20land%20acquisition%20process%20and%20the%20intricacies%20that%20follows%20and%20how%20much%20each%20of%20us%20as%20DC%20does%20to%20bring%20all%20land%20acquisition%20matter%20to%20close%20and%20bring%20forth%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Lokayukta%20is%20an%20oversight%20body%2C%20meant%20to%20look%20at%20corruption.%20It%20faults%20your%20actions%20on%20procedure.%20What%20do%20you%20propose%20to%20do%20next%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArmstrong%20Pame%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20While%20I%20would%20not%20like%20to%20question%20the%20jurisdictions%20and%20the%20methods%20adopted%20by%20Lokayukta%20to%20arrive%20at%20the%20preliminary%20report%2C%20it%20is%20true%20that%20the%20Lokayukta%20is%20to%20look%20into%20the%20allegation%20of%20corruption%20rather%20than%20the%20procedures%20of%20land%20acquisition%20and%20I%20am%20sure%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Lokayukta%20would%20do%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20am%20yet%20to%20receive%20any%20official%20intimation%20from%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Lokayukta%2C%20so%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20comment%20much%20on%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20furnishing%20these%20facts%20based%20on%20some%20reports%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-lokayukta-ias-officer%5C%22%3Ecarried%20by%20%3Cem%3ET%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Ehe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20August%206%2C%202023.%20As%20stated%20in%20the%20above%20few%20court%20cases%20mentioned%2C%20all%20acts%20done%20by%20me%20in%20the%20official%20capacity%20as%20District%20Collector%20of%20Tamenglong%20have%20been%20justified%20by%20the%20competent%20court.%20While%20I%20still%20have%20faith%20in%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Lokayukta%20that%20such%20malicious%20complaints%20would%20be%20outrightly%20rejected%20because%20if%20all%20such%20fictitious%20complaints%20are%20to%20be%20entertained%2C%20we%20would%20not%20see%20the%20progress%20of%20the%20railways%20as%20we%20have%20witnessed%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20competent%20and%20honest%20officer%20would%20be%20willing%20to%20take%20up%20any%20decision%20in%20the%20future%20if%20such%20complaints%20are%20continued%20to%20be%20entertained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20any%20legal%20battle%2C%20there%20can%20only%20be%20one%20party%20that%20emerges%20victorious.%20If%20the%20aggrieved%20party%20continues%20to%20endlessly%20fight%20in%20all%20available%20forums%2C%20they%20are%20simply%20wasting%20time%2C%20energy%2C%20resources%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20the%20zeal%20of%20the%20officer%20to%20serve%20the%20nation.%20In%20this%20matter%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Marangjing%20have%20taken%20up%20protests%20against%20me%20in%20all%20possible%20forums%2C%20carried%20out%20strikes%2C%20and%20even%20burnt%20my%20effigies.%20Having%20gone%20through%20all%20these%2C%20I%20would%20say%20my%20morale%20is%20definitely%20down%20but%20I%20would%20have%20to%20keep%20fighting%20as%20I%20believe%20my%20commitment%20towards%20the%20development%20of%20the%20nation%20is%20bigger%20than%20their%20hatred%20and%20jealousy%20against%20me.%20In%20all%20of%20these%2C%20I%20hope%20that%20all%20the%20people%20in%20the%20system%2C%20including%20my%20well-wishers%20and%20the%20media%2C%20will%20continue%20to%20stand%20for%20the%20truth%20and%20stand%20the%20test%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20me%20this%20was%20already%20a%20concluded%20matter.%20The%20Maringjing%20village%20took%20up%20this%20matter%20again%20only%20after%20almost%20a%20gap%20of%20four%20years%2C%20knowing%20fully%20well%20that%20I%20am%20no%20longer%20in%20Manipur%2C%20leaving%20me%20defenceless%2C%20without%20being%20physically%20present.%20Such%20a%20calculated%20move%20by%20the%20Maringjing%20village%20was%20never%20expected%20as%20I%20thought%20we%20parted%20ways%20on%20good%20terms.%20It%20looks%20like%20this%20village%20is%20now%20committed%20to%20destroying%20my%20career%20no%20matter%20what.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20many%20more%20cases%20they%20will%20put%20up.%20But%20as%20long%20as%20it%20is%20a%20legal%20battle%2C%20I%20am%20sure%20of%20winning%20them%20all%2C%20because%20I%20had%20done%20it%20in%20the%20best%20interest%20of%20the%20state%20and%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%20the%20fruit%20of%20such%20hard%20work%20by%20all%20of%20us%2C%20including%20many%20officers%20%5Bwho%20worked%5D%20before%20and%20after%20me%2C%20is%20being%20seen%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20railways%20coming%20to%20Manipur%20especially%2C%20in%20this%20time%20of%20crisis%20where%20essential%20commodities%20are%20carried%20on%20trains%20in%20bulk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13122920%2Fimage-1217.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22874%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%