on%20conducted%20experiments%20to%20establish%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20chloroform%20as%20an%20anesthetic%20to%20treat%20patients.%20It%20was%20a%20major%20breakthrough%20that%20led%20to%20several%20lives%20being%20saved%20in%20the%20future.%20While%20the%20chemical%20was%20being%20used%20for%20surgical%20procedures%2C%20this%20trial%20helped%20in%20determining%20how%20it%20could%20be%20used%20safely.%20The%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20report%20would%20go%20on%20to%20be%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Lancet%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilt%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20floods%20and%20a%20plague%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2023-08-11T143636.627-1691745341.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20tamarind%20tree%20that%20saved%20the%20lives%20of%20150%20people%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2023-08-11T143636.627-1691745341.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2023-08-11T143636.627-1691745341-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2023-08-11T143636.627-1691745341-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2023-08-11T143636.627-1691745341-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2023-08-11T143636.627-1691745341-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327029%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20tamarind%20tree%20that%20saved%20the%20lives%20of%20150%20people%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20medicine%20flourished%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20unprecedented%20rainfall%20resulted%20in%20catastrophic%20floods%2C%20ravaging%20the%20erstwhile%20princely%20state.%20During%20the%20reign%20of%20the%20sixth%20Nizam%2C%20one%20of%20the%20casualties%20of%20the%20Musi%20River%20flooding%20was%20the%20Afzal%20Gunj%20Hospital.%20More%20than%2015%2C000%20people%20lost%20their%20lives%2C%20but%20a%20large%20tamarind%20tree%20near%20the%20hospital%20acted%20as%20a%20savior%20for%20150%20people%20who%20climbed%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201911%2C%20Mir%20Osman%20Ali%20Khan%2C%20Hyderabad%E2%80%99s%20last%20Nizam%20took%20over.%20This%20is%20when%20the%20bubonic%20plague%20hit%20Hyderabad.%20This%20epidemic%20yet%20again%20took%20several%20lives%2C%20and%20brought%20to%20the%20fore%20the%20need%20for%20a%20major%20infrastructure%20revamp.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOsman%20Ali%20Khan%20is%20said%20to%20have%20heralded%20a%20new%20modern%20infrastructure%20push%20that%20would%20be%20better%20equipped%20to%20deal%20with%20nature%E2%80%99s%20fury.%20In%201912%2C%20Hyderabad%20got%20its%20first%20urban%20development%20authority%2C%20the%20Hyderabad%20City%20Improvement%20Board%20(CIB).%20From%20then%20on%2C%20the%20city%20saw%20several%20new%20constructions%2C%20including%20buildings%2C%20roads%2C%20bridges%2C%20sewers%2C%20railways%2C%20parks%2C%20dams%2C%20courts%2C%20universities%20and%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Musi%20river%20flooded%2C%20Osman%20Ali%20Khan%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20initiated%20the%20construction%20of%20two%20reservoirs%20%E2%80%94%20Osman%20Sagar%20and%20Himayat%20Sagar%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F115487%2Fmokshagundam-visvesvaraya-hyderabad-flood-engineer-day%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eby%20Sir%20M%20Visvesvaraya%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20even%20before%20he%20came%20to%20power.%20Many%20heritage%20structures%2C%20including%20the%20Osmania%20General%20Hospital%2C%20Hyderabad%20High%20Court%2C%20Government%20City%20College%2C%20Kacheguda%20railway%20station%20and%20Osmania%20University%20were%20built%20by%20the%20Last%20Nizam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAn%20unmissable%20part%20of%20old%20Hyderabad%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201440px)%20100vw%2C%201440px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FEb6zDzZVAAAlMii-1691745819.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20illustration%20of%20the%20hospital%20signed%20by%20Vincent%20Esch%2C%20which%20was%20auctioned%20by%20Christie's%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FEb6zDzZVAAAlMii-1691745819.jpg%201440w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FEb6zDzZVAAAlMii-1691745819-300x133.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FEb6zDzZVAAAlMii-1691745819-500x222.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FEb6zDzZVAAAlMii-1691745819-768x341.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FEb6zDzZVAAAlMii-1691745819-150x67.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327031%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAn%20illustration%20of%20the%20hospital%20signed%20by%20Vincent%20Esch%2C%20which%20was%20auctioned%20by%20Christie%E2%80%99s%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201919%2C%20the%20Nizam%20commissioned%20British%20architect%20Vincent%20Esch%20to%20design%20a%20hospital%20equipped%20with%20modern%20facilities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEsch%20was%20known%20as%20the%20pioneer%20of%20the%20Indo-Saracenic%20style%20of%20architecture%2C%20which%20combined%20elements%20from%20Mughal%20architecture%20with%20the%20British%20style.%20The%20architect%20had%20earlier%20worked%20on%20the%20Victoria%20Memorial%20in%20Calcutta.%20In%20a%20report%20on%20Esch%2C%20writer%20and%20lecturer%20GHR%20Tillotson%20calls%20this%20style%2C%20%E2%80%9Can%20attempt%20by%20British%20architects%20in%20India%2C%20beginning%20in%20the%20last%20third%20of%20the%20nineteenth%20century%2C%20to%20develop%20a%20style%20which%20reflected%20the%20local%20architectural%20heritage%2C%20and%20so%20to%20present%20an%20Indian%20imagery%20for%20the%20buildings%20of%20the%20Raj%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETillotson%20adds%20that%20Esch%20described%20his%20style%20used%20in%20Hyderabad%20as%C2%A0%20%E2%80%98Perpendicular%20Mogul%20Saracenic%E2%80%99.%20%E2%80%9CEsch%20regarded%20the%20style%20he%20used%20in%20Hyderabad%20as%20a%20slight%20departure%20from%20strict%20Mughal%20design%2C%20and%20used%20this%20term%20which%20acknowledges%20a%20visually%20evident%20Gothic%20influence%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Tillotson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFlanking%20the%20left%20bank%20of%20the%20Musi%20River%2C%20Osmania%20General%20Hospital%20was%20built%20on%2026.5%20acres%20of%20land.%20What%20catches%20your%20eye%20when%20you%20see%20the%20majestic%20structure%20are%20the%20huge%20bulbous%20domes%2C%20which%20are%20an%20unmissable%20part%20of%20Old%20City%E2%80%99s%20skyline.%20The%20hospital%20reportedly%20cost%20Rs%2020%20lakh%20to%20build%20and%20the%20construction%20was%20completed%20in%201925.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20building%2C%20which%20is%20the%20one%20activists%20want%20to%20save%2C%20was%20constructed%20using%20granite%2C%20limestone%20and%20lime%20plaster.%20The%20three-storied%20building%20has%20a%20jack%20arch%20roof%20that%20is%20supported%20by%20iron%20girders%2C%20and%20is%20said%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20early%20examples%20of%20smaller%20reinforced%20cement%20concrete%20slabs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20plan%20and%20construction%20might%20be%20British%2C%20the%20grand%20dome%2C%20cupolas%2C%20historical%20motifs%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Echajjas%20%3C%2Fem%3Egive%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F157345%2Fmughal-emperor-mughlai-food-history-india-news%2F%5C%22%3EMughal%20touch%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20was%20also%20a%20park%2C%20nurses%E2%80%99%20quarters%20(in%20case%20of%20quarantine)%2C%20and%20a%20block%20for%20laundry%2C%20which%20were%20later%20demolished%20to%20make%20way%20for%20in-patient%20treatments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%201%2C168-bed%20hospital%20campus%20also%20includes%20a%20nursing%20and%20dental%20college.%20It%20is%20also%20one%20of%20the%20only%20tertiary%20hospitals%20in%20the%20old%20city%20that%20the%20poor%20from%20nearby%20districts%20also%20have%20access%20to.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20fight%20to%20retain%20an%20icon%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2023-08-11T143620.203-1691745943.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20hospital%20is%20spread%20across%2026.5%20acres%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2023-08-11T143620.203-1691745943.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2023-08-11T143620.203-1691745943-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2023-08-11T143620.203-1691745943-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2023-08-11T143620.203-1691745943-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2023-08-11T143620.203-1691745943-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327033%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20hospital%20is%20spread%20across%2026.5%20acres.%20Image%3A%20The%20Deccan%20Archive%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202020%2C%20the%20heritage%20block%20at%20the%20OGH%20was%20flooded%20and%20subsequently%20vacated.%20Continuous%20rains%20left%20the%20wards%20in%20the%20heritage%20building%20filled%20with%20ankle-deep%20water.%20It%20was%20sealed%20and%20vacated%20after%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudents%20and%20doctors%20have%20been%20demanding%20urgent%20repairs%20for%20a%20long%20time%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20all%20OMC%20(Osmania%20Medical%20College)%20students%20have%20faced%20problems%20while%20studying%20at%20OGH.%20Almost%20every%20corner%20or%20room%20has%20patches%20of%20roof%20that%20have%20collapsed%20over%20the%20years.%20They%20make%20temporary%20repairs%2C%20but%20in%20the%20rainy%20season%2C%20these%20issues%20worsen.%20There%20is%20always%20a%20heavy%20influx%20of%20patients%20and%20if%20we%20need%20to%20provide%20better%20services%2C%20then%20we%20need%20better%20maintenance%20of%20the%20building%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dr%20Kadali%20Vishni%2C%20who%20passed%20out%20from%20OMC%20in%202014%20to%20The%20News%20Minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20led%20to%20a%20renewed%20push%20by%20politicians%20to%20demolish%20the%20structure%20and%20build%20a%20new%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20everyone%20unanimously%20agrees%20upon%2C%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20building%20is%20in%20urgent%20need%20of%20repair%20and%20restoration.%20While%20Telangana%20Chief%20Minister%20K%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%20wants%20the%20entire%20structure%20to%20be%20demolished%2C%20conservation%20architects%20want%20it%20to%20be%20restored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-twitter%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22500