ng%20another%20significant%20milestone%20in%20its%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%206%20August%2C%202023%2C%20it%20entered%20a%20translunar%20orbit%2C%20starting%20its%20journey%20towards%20the%20Moon%20after%20completing%20several%20Earth%20orbits%20since%20it%20was%20launched%20on%2014%20July%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20shared%20by%20ISRO%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20shows%20the%20visuals%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F193167%2Fisro-chandrayaan2-pictures-moon-crater-sisir-mitra-scientist-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Moon%E2%80%99s%20surface%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20various%20angles%2C%20captured%20by%20Chandrayaan-3%20during%20the%20Lunar%20Orbit%20Insertion%20(LOI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20Moon%2C%20as%20viewed%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FChandrayaan3%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Chandrayaan3%3C%2Fa%3E%20spacecraft%20during%20Lunar%20Orbit%20Insertion%20(LOI)%20on%20August%205%2C%202023.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FISRO%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23ISRO%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FxQtVyLTu0c%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FxQtVyLTu0c%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20LVM3-M4%2FCHANDRAYAAN-3%20MISSION%20(%40chandrayaan_3)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchandrayaan_3%2Fstatus%2F1688215948531015681%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%206%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20spacecraft%20successfully%20underwent%20a%20planned%20orbit%20reduction%20manoeuvre.%20The%20retrofitting%20of%20engines%20brought%20it%20closer%20to%20the%20moon%E2%80%99s%20surface%2C%20now%20to%20170%20km%20x%204313%20km.%20The%20next%20operation%20to%20further%20reduce%20the%20orbit%20is%20scheduled%20f