inable-plastic-free-kitchenware-cutlery-sugarcane-palm%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elife%20and%20sustainability.%3C%2Fa%3E%20We%20would%20chat%20about%20how%20we%20could%20do%20something%20about%20it%20and%20ended%20up%20brainstorming%20ideas%20for%20hours.%20Being%20in%20the%20media%20industry%2C%20both%20of%20us%20were%20exposed%20first-hand%20to%20innovators%20around%20the%20world%20who%20were%20working%20in%20the%20sustainability%20field.%20We%20often%20heard%20topics%20like%20solar%20energy%2C%20upcycling%2C%20reusing%2C%20and%20recycling%20around%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLooking%20at%20so%20many%20people%20working%20towards%20sustainability%2C%20we%20thought%2C%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Hum%20bhi%20kar%20sakte%20hai%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3E(we%20can%20do%20it%20too).%20So%20in%202013%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20leap%20of%20faith%2C%E2%80%9D%20Madhuri%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20started%2C%20the%20concept%20of%20sustainability%20and%20carbon%20footprint%20was%20not%20as%20popular%20as%20today.%20People%20were%20not%20as%20well-informed%20about%20the%20harm%20we%20do%20to%20the%20environment%2C%20and%20many%20did%20not%20care%20about%20what%20happened%20to%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCvcsr95toXk%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCvcsr95toXk%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3